quran[1606]{c,v,t}:
  50,1,Qaaf. Mi woondirii Alqur'aanaare teddunde nden
  50,2,"Si ko woni, ɓe ŋalɗu ko tawi kon jertinoowo arii ɓe iwɗo e maɓɓe ; heeferɓe ɓen wi'i: \"Ɗum ɗoo ko huunde haawniinde"
  50,3,"Kere si men maayii, men wontii mbulmbuldi...? Ɗum ɗon ko ruttitagol woɗɗungol non"
  50,4,Gomɗii Meɗen anndi ko leydi ndin ñaamata kon e maɓɓe ; hino ka Amen gaa deftere reenunde
  50,5,"Si ko woni, ɓe fennu goonga kan tuma nde ka arunoo e maɓɓe, hiɓe e nder fiyaaku jilɓuɗo"
  50,6,"E ɓee ndaaraali kammu ngun dow maɓɓe, ko honno Men mahiri ngun Men cuɗini ngu ; hara perɗi alanaa ngu"
  50,7,"Leydi ndin kadi, Men weerti ndi Men werlii e mayri pelle, Men fuɗini e mayri kala nooneeji [puɗi] wooɗuɗi"
  50,8,fii tasakuyee e waaju wonannde kala jeyaaɗo ruttotooɗo
  50,9,"Men jippini kadi ndiyam barkinaaɗam ummaade ka kammu, Men fuɗiniri ɗam gese e gabbe soñeteeɗe"
  50,10,e leɗɗe tamaro juutuɗe wonduɗe e piindi fawondirndi
  50,11,ko arsike jeyaaɓe ɓen. Men wuurnitiri ɗam kadi leydi yoorundi. Awa ko non woni fii ummital ngal
  50,12,"Ado maɓɓe, yimɓe nuuhu ɓen, e yimɓe Ɓunndu ɓen e Samuuda'en [fow] fennuno"
  50,13,"e 'Aadi'en, e Fir'awna e musiɗɓe Luutu ɓen"
  50,14,"e yimɓe fitaare nden, e yimɓe Tubba' ɓen. Kala maɓɓe fennuno Nulaaɓe ɓen, kammbaa Am on jojji"
  50,15,"Kere Men ronkuno fii tagu aranu ngun? Ko woni kamɓe, hiɓe e jiɓaare fii tagiteede laawol kesol"
  50,16,"Gomɗii Men tagii neɗɗanke on, Meɗen anndi ko wonkii makko kin sowinsinirta mo. Ko Menen ɓuri ɓadaade mo e dii ɗaɗol (makko) daande ngol"
  50,17,"tuma nde jaɓɓoytooɓe ɓen ɗiɗo jaɓɓoroytoo [golle makko ɗen] ñaamo e nano, hara hiɓe jooɗii"
  50,18,"O wowlataa konngol, si wanaa hino takko makko winndoowo tawaaɗo"
  50,19,"Ɗeɗɗere maayde nden ardi e goonga : \"Ko ɗum wonunoo ko dogaynoɗaa"
  50,20,Wuttee ka alaandu ; ko nden woni Ñalaande kammbaa nden
  50,21,"Wonkii kala ara, hara hiki wonndi e soggoowo e seedotooɗo"
  50,22,Gomɗii a laatinoke welsindiiɗo e ndee. Men hunci wirngallo maa ngon kisan; gite maa ɗen hannde ko seeɓuɗe
  50,23,"Wonndiiɗo makko on wi'a: \"Ko ɗum ɗoo woni ka am ɗoo, maandinaa-ɗum"
  50,24,"Bugee ka Jahannama onon ɗiɗo, kala yedduɗo canndallo"
  50,25,"haɗoowo moƴƴere, jaggitoowo, sikkitiiɗo"
  50,26,on waɗiduɗo e Allah reweteeɗo goo. Bugee mo ka nder lepte saɗtuɗe
  50,27,"Cinndadiijo makko (seytaane) on wi'i: \"Joomi amen, mi bewinaali oo; si ko woni, ko e majjere woɗɗunde o wonunoo e mun"
  50,28,"[Allah] daala : \"Wata on yeddondir ka Am ɗoo ! Nde tawnoo Mi ardiniino e mon kammbaa"
  50,29,Konngol waɗtitetaake ka Am ɗoo ; Mi siforaa kadi tooñoowo jeyaaɓe ɓen
  50,30,"Ñalnde Men wi'anoyta Jahannama on : \"E a heewii?\" Nge wi'a: \"Ko ɓeydee hino woodi"
  50,31,"Aljanna on ɓaɗtinanee gomɗuɓe ɓen, hara wanaa ka woɗɗi"
  50,32,"Ko ɗum ɗoo woni ko fodaɗon, wonannde kala ruttiiɗo [e Joomi mun] reeniiɗo"
  50,33,"on huluɗo Jom Hinaranke On ka wirnii, o ardi e ɓernde laaɓunde"
  50,34,"Naatiree mo e jam\". Ko nden woni ñalaande luttaynde nden"
  50,35,"Hino woodani ɓe ton kala ko ɓe faaletee, hara kadi ɓeydaari hino ka Amen"
  50,36,"Ɗuuɗii e gire ɗen Men halki ado maɓɓe, ko ɓen ɓurnooɓe doole, ɓen wanngorii e leydi ndin, ndaarugol taw si ɓe heɓay laaworde"
  50,37,"Pellet, wonii e ɗum, waaju wonannde kala jom ɓernde, maa tuɗuɗo noppi hara ko tawaaɗo"
  50,38,"Gomɗii Men tagii kammuuli ɗin e leydi ndin e kon ko woni hakkunde majji, nder balɗe jeegoo, tampere woo heɓaali Men. @Corrected"
  50,39,"Muñño e ko ɓe wowlata kon, subbunhinanoɗaa Joomi maa ado puɗal naange ngen e ado mutal ngal"
  50,40,"Jemma on kadi, subbunhinanoɗaa Mo e ka battane [julɗe] farlaaɗe"
  50,41,"Heɗo, ñalnde noddoowo on noddoyta e nokkuure ɓadiinde"
  50,42,"ñalnde ɓe naniroyta haacaango ngon e hoore goonga. Ko nden woni Ñalnnde yaltugol ngol [ka genaale]"
  50,43,"Pellet, ko Menen wuurnata Men wara, ko ka Amen kadi woni ruttorde nden"
  50,44,"Ñalnde leydi ndin seekotoo [ɓe yaltira] heñagol; ko nde woni mooɓirde newaniinde Men"
  50,45,"Ko Menen ɓuri anndude ko ɓe wowlata kon. A wonaa dooloowoɓe. Haray waajor Alqur'aanaare nden, kala huloowo kammbaa An on"
  51,1,Mi woondirii keneeli jarorayɗi (leydi) jaragol
  51,2,Mi woondirii duule ronndotooɗe toɓo tiiɗngo
  51,3,Mi woondirii laaɗe dogirayɗe newaare
  51,4,E peccooji yamiraande
  51,5,"ko podete ɗon ko, ko goongo"
  51,6,Haasbeede ko ko wonata
  51,7,Mi woondirii kammu jom ɗate ngun
  51,8,"Pellet, hiɗon e konngol luurrangol"
  51,9,Hino yiltee e makko kala firlitaaɗo e gomɗinal
  51,10,Fenooɓe ɓen huɗaama
  51,11,ɓen yolliiɓe e majjere welsindiiɓe
  51,12,"Hiɓe lamndoo : \"Ko honnde woni Ñalaande njoɓdi kuuɗe"
  51,13,Ñalaande nde ɓe leptoyteeɓe ka Yiite
  51,14,Meeɗee lepte mon ɗen; ko ɗum woni ko keppatnoɗon kon
  51,15,"Pellet, gomɗuɓe ɓen wonii e aljannaaji e ɓulli"
  51,16,Jaggatnooɓe ko Joom maɓɓe okkiɓe ɓe te ko adii ɗuum koɓe moƴƴinatnooɓe
  51,17,Hoɓe pamɗuno koɓe ɗaanatoo jemma
  51,18,E saanga ndoogu hoɓe toro yaafeede
  51,19,Ina e jawɗe mumen hakke wonande ñaagatooɓe e ɓe ñaagataako
  51,20,Ina e nder leydi he maandeeji wonande yananaaɓe
  51,21,E nder pittaali mon mate on teskataaka
  51,22,Ina e kammu arsuka mon e ko podante ɗon
  51,23,E Joom kammu e leydi koɗum goongo hono no kaalirton nih
  51,24,Mbela arii e maa yeewtere hoɗɓe Ibraahiima teddinaaɓe
  51,25,"Tuma ɓe naatunoo ka makko ɓe wi'i: \"Salaam (Kisiyee mon)\". O maaki: \"Menen ko men ɗenƴii ɓe on"
  51,26,O naayii faade e koreeji makko O addori ngaari payndi
  51,27,O ɓadaniɓe ndi o wii on ñaamata
  51,28,"O so*i e mum en kulol, ɓe wii woto hul, ɓe weltiniriɓe cuklel"
  51,29,"Jom suudu makko ari hombo wulla o hellii yeesa makko, o wii nayeejo dimara"
  51,30,Malaykaaji ɗi mbii ko hono nih Joom ma daali ko Kanko woni ñeeño Ganndo
  51,31,"[Annabai Ibraahiima] maaki: \"Ko woni fii mon, onon ɓee nelaaɓe"
  51,32,"Ɓe wi'i: \"Menen men nela e yimɓe bomɓe ɓen"
  51,33,"fii yo men accitu e maɓɓe, kaaƴe iwɗe e loope (juɗaaɗe)"
  51,34,"maandiniraaɗe ka Joomi maa, fii fantinooɓe ɓen"
  51,35,Men yaltini toon kala gomɗimɓe wonunooɓe ton
  51,36,"Men tawaano ton, si wanaa suudu juulɓe wooturu"
  51,37,"Men acci ton maande, wonannde ɓen hulooɓe lepte muusuɗe ɗen"
  51,38,"[Men acci kadi maande] e Muusaa, tuma nde Men nulunoo mo e Fir'awna, wonndude e hujja ɓannguɗo"
  51,39,"Kono o ɗuurnodii e cemmbe makko, o wi'i [Muusaa]: \"Ko mbileejo maa feetuɗo"
  51,40,"Men nanngi mo kanko e koneeli makko ɗin, Men bugodii ɓe ka maayo, tawde ko o felniiɗo"
  51,41,"E 'Adi'en, tuma Men wurtunoo henndu bonndu ndun e maɓɓe"
  51,42,"ndu accataa hay huunde nde ndu arani, si wanaa ndu waɗtay nde wa ndoondi"
  51,43,"E Samuuda'en kadi, tuma nde ɓe wi'ananoo : \"Dakmitee haa seeɗa"
  51,44,"Ɓe townitanii yamiroore Joomi maɓɓe nden, haacaango ngon nanngi ɓe, tawi hiɓe ƴeewa"
  51,45,"Ɓe waawaano daragol (laawoo), ɓe wonaano kadi faabaaɓe"
  51,46,"Ko non kadi yimɓe Nuuhu ɓen ko adii[ɓe]. Ɓen ko yimɓe faasiqiiɓe wonunoo"
  51,47,"Kammu ngun, Men mahir ngu doole Amen. Pellet, ko Men yaññuɓe"
  51,48,"Leydi ndin kan, Men weertundi. Men moƴƴii weertuɓe"
  51,49,"E kala huunde, Men tagii noone ɗiɗi; belajo'o on waajitoray"
  51,50,"Awa dogee kisan faade e Allah. Min, wonannde on immorde ka Makko, ko mi jertinoowo ɓannguɗo"
  51,51,"Wata on waɗidane Allah reweteeɗo goo. Min, wonannde on immorde ka Makko, ko mi jertinoowo ɓannguɗo"
  51,52,"Ko wano non. Nulaaɗo araali e ɓen adinooɓe ɓe, si wanaa ɓe wi'ay : \"Ko mbileejo maa feetuɗo"
  51,53,"Hara ɓe wasondir e ɗum? Ko woni kon, ɓee ko yimɓe bewuɓe"
  51,54,"Runto ɓe, a felnaaki [e fiiaɓɓe]"
  51,55,"Waajo tun; sabu waajagol ngol, hino nafa gomɗimɓe ɓen"
  51,56,"Mi tagiraali jinna e yimɓe, si wanaa fii yo ɓe rewan"
  51,57,Mi ɗaɓɓiraa ɓe arsike; Mi ɗaɓɓaa yo ɓe ñammina
  51,58,"Pellet, ko Allah woni arsikoowo On, Jom cemmbe tiiɗuɗe"
  51,59,"Haray hino woodani ɓen tooñuɓe, bakkaat yeru bakkaat nanndo maɓɓe'en, wata ɓe hawju"
  51,60,"Bone woodanii ɓen yedduɓe, e nden Ñalaande maɓɓe nde ɓe kammbanaa"
  52,1,"Mi woondirii [Fello] Tuuri ngon"
  52,2,E Deftere winndaande nden
  52,3,e ɗeri fontaaɗi
  52,4,E Suudu wuurniraandu ndun
  52,5,E Kippoodi toowundi ndin
  52,6,E maayo heewuno ngon
  52,7,"Pellet, lepte Joomi maa ɗen ko yanooje"
  52,8,Alaa duñoowo ɗe
  52,9,Ñalnde kammu ngun dillirta dillere
  52,10,pelle ɗen wona e yahugol
  52,11,"haray nden ñalnde, bone woodanii fennuɓe ɓen"
  52,12,"ɓen wonuɓe e jumpugol, hiɓe fija"
  52,13,Ñalnde ɓe duñiroytee doole ka Yiite Jahannama duñannde
  52,14,"[Ɓe wi'anee] : \"Ko ngee Yiite woni ko fennaynoɗon"
  52,15,E ko mbilewu nii? Kaa hara on alaa yi'ude
  52,16,"Sumee e magge! Muññiɗon maa on muññaaki, fow no fota e mon. Anndee ko yoɓeteɗon, ko kon ko gollaynoɗon"
  52,17,"Pellet, gomɗuɓe ɓen hino e Aljannaaji e neemaaji"
  52,18,"ko ɓe dakimitotooɓe kon ko Joomi maɓɓe okki ɓe, Joomi maɓɓe daɗndi ɓe lepte Jahiimi ɗen"
  52,19,"[Ɓe wi'anee] : \"Ñaamee yaron, ko newi moɗdeum, sabu kon ko gollaynoɗon"
  52,20,"hara ko on soɓɓindiiɓe e hoore danɗe weertindiraaɗe\", Men resina ɓe kadi yooɗa e yaaJa giteeɓe"
  52,21,"Ɓen gomɗimɓe, geyngol maɓɓe ngol kadi jokki ɓe e gomɗinal, Men tawtindinay ɓe e geyngol maɓɓe ngol. Men ɗuytantaa ɓe huunde e golle maɓɓe ɗen; neɗɗo kala ko faggitii kon no tiginaa"
  52,22,Men ɓeydani ɓe muuyanteeɗi e tebbeeli kala ko tuuyetee
  52,23,"Hiɓe jaaɓondira ton, ñedduɗe ɗe jillaa meere wanaa ko bakkondinta"
  52,24,"Sukaaɓe no eltanaaɓe hino wanngoo hakkunde maɓɓe, wa'uɓe wa kaŋŋe maraaɗe"
  52,25,"Yoga maɓɓe fewtita yoga, ɓe lamndondira"
  52,26,"ɓe wi'a: \"Pellet, men laatino ado [hannde], hulunooɓe [lepte ɗen] hakkunde yimɓe amen"
  52,27,"Allah moƴƴii e amen, O daɗni men lepte Norngal"
  52,28,"Men laatino ado [hannde], torotonooɓe Mo. Pellet, ko Kanko woni Moƴƴo, Hinnotooɗo On"
  52,29,"Anndintin tun, sabu neema Joomi maa on, a wonaa ndureejo wanaa a feetuɗo"
  52,30,"Kaa ɓe wi'ay wonnde : \"Ko yimoowo ! Men habbitani mo tun jikke maayde"
  52,31,"Maaku : \"Awa habbitee ! Min kadi miɗo habbitodi e mon"
  52,32,Kaa ko haqqille maɓɓe ɗen yamirɓe ɗum? Kaa hara ko ɓe yimɓe bewuɓe tun
  52,33,"Kaa ɓe wi'ay wonnde : \"O sincu nde?\" Si ko woni, wanaa ɓe gomɗinooɓe"
  52,34,"Awa yo ɓe addii yewtere sugu mayre, si wonii ko ɓe goonguɓe"
  52,35,Kaa ɓe tagira ɓaawo taguɗo? Kaa ko kamɓe woni taguɓe ɓen
  52,36,"Kaa (ko) kamɓe tagi kammuuli ɗin e leydi ndin? Ko woni kon, ɓe yananaaka"
  52,37,Kaa ɓe jogiti ngaluuji Joomi maa ɗin? Kaa ko kamɓe woni huɓindiiɓe ɓen
  52,38,Kaa ɓe jogiti ɓargal ngal ɓe jentorta? Awa yo heɗitiiɗo maɓɓe on addu hujja ɓannguɗo
  52,39,"Kaa hara ko ɓiɗɓe rewɓe woodanta Mo, onon kan worɓe ɓen"
  52,40,"Kaa a lamndi ɓe njoɓdi, hara yoɓugol ndi no teddani ɓe"
  52,41,"Kaa ɓe anndu fii wirniiɗi ɗin, hara hiɓe winnda"
  52,42,"Kaa ɓe faala fewjoore? Doo ko yedduɓe ɓen, woni fooleteeɓe pewje ɓen"
  52,43,"Kaa hiɓe mari reweteeɗo ko woori Allah? Senaade woodanii Allah, e kon ko ɓe sirkata"
  52,44,"Si ɓe yi'ii taƴatine immornde ka kammu no yani, ɓe wi'a: \"Ko duule fawondirɗe"
  52,45,"Terto ɓe, haa ɓe hawroya e ñalaande maɓɓe nde ɓe leptoytee e mun"
  52,46,"Ñalnde nde pewje maɓɓe duncanoytaa ɓe hay huunde, ɓe wonaa kadi walloyteeɓe"
  52,47,"Ko pellet, hino woodani tooñuɓe ɓen, lepte goo ko wanaa ɗen ɗon. Kono ko ɓuri ɗuuɗude kon e maɓɓe, ɓe anndaa"
  52,48,"Muñño ñaawoore Joomi maa nden. Tawde pellet, hiɗa e ndenka Amen. Seniniraa yettugol Joomi maa, tuma ɓaŋotoɗaa"
  52,49,"Jemma on kadi, subbunhinanoɗaa Mo e ka mutugol koode"
  53,1,E hoodere si konde fukkiima
  53,2,Gondiijo mon majjaani o bewaañi
  53,3,O haalata belaaɗe
  53,4,"Ndee [Alqur’aanaare] wonaali, si wanaa waaju bahyateeɗo"
  53,5,Ko jom semmbe janngini ɗum mbo
  53,6,Jom mbaadi njoondi o fotondiri
  53,7,Hombo e jookli toowɗi
  53,8,Refti o ɓadi o ɓattii
  53,9,O woni ɓadiiɗo fotde laanye ɗiɗe wolla ko ɓuri ɓadaade
  53,10,O wahyii e maccuɗo makko ko O wahyii ko
  53,11,ɓernde mum fennaani ko o yi*i ko
  53,12,mbela haɗa yeddandira e Mum ko O yi*i
  53,13,Ko noon tigi o yi*ii Jibriir laawol goɗngol
  53,14,ka lekki sidar njani sanne
  53,15,ka kiin lekki woni aljanna koɗirɗo
  53,16,Nde muurata e lekki sidra-he ko naatata
  53,17,Yitere oonñaaki nde yawtaani keerol
  53,18,Ko goonga o yi*ii e kaawsaaji Alla ɓurɗi mawnude
  53,19,Onon heeferɓe mbela on nji*ii laata e ujjaa
  53,20,E manaata tataɓiija goɗɗo o
  53,21,Mbela na woodani on gorko na woodani Mbo debbo
  53,22,ɗuum de wadde ko feccoore nde nuunɗaani
  53,23,ɗi ngonah si wonah inɗe ɗe innuɗon onon e baabiraaɓe mon Alla jippinaani heen daliil ɓe ndewaani si wonah sikke e mbelamme pittaali ko goongo peewal arii e maɓɓe ummaade to Joom mum en
  53,24,wolla mbela na woodani neɗɗo ko o wooɗa ko
  53,25,Ko Alla woodani ko sakkati e ko adii
  53,26,Heewii e malaykaaji e nder kammuuji ɗi tefoore majji nafatah huunde tawi wonah caggal de Alla sakkitani wonande mbo O wela O
  53,27,Pellet ɓeen ɓe ngoonɗinaani laakira hoɓe innira malaykaaji inɗe rewɓe
  53,28,"Woodanaani ɓe ganndal, alah kove ndewata si wonah sikke, pellet sikke nafatah e goonga hay huunde"
  53,29,ɗuurno oon nduntiiɗa jikru amen mbo yiɗah si wonah nguurndam aduna
  53,30,"Ko ɗoon ganndal mum en haaɗi, pellet ko Alla ɓuri anndude oon majjuɗo laawol Makko, ko Kanko kadi ɓuri anndude oon peewɗo"
  53,31,"Ko Alla woodani kala ko woni e kammuuji e leydi ngam o yoɓa ɓeen bonnuɓe koɓe mbonni ko, O yoɓa kadi moƴƴinɓe ko moƴƴi"
  53,32,"ɓen woɗɗitotooɓe bakkatuuji mawɗi ɗin e pankare [ɓe faggitotaako] si wanaa tokoosi ɗin. Pellet, Joomi maa ko yaajuɗo yaafuyee. Ko Kanko ɓuri anndude on gila O fuɗɗunoo on ummaade e leydi, e nde wonunoɗon fuƴƴannde ka deedi neeniraaɓe mon. Wata on mantu ko'e mon; ko Kanko ɓuri anndude gomɗuɓe ɓen"
  53,33,E a tinaali ɗuurniiɗo on
  53,34,"hino okka seeɗaa, hooti o ɗawa"
  53,35,Kere o jogi ganndal wirniiɗi ngal o yiirata
  53,36,Kaa o humpitaaka ko woni kon e ɗeri Muusa ɗin
  53,37,"e [ka ɗeri] Ibraahiima hunnuɗo [ahadi yottini]"
  53,38,"wonnde wonkii [woo] ronndotaako doŋgal (bakkaatu) wokkii goo"
  53,39,"e wonnde alanaa neɗɗanke, si wonaa ko o golli kon"
  53,40,"e wonnde golle makko ɗen, aray ka yi'ee"
  53,41,refti o yoɓiree ɗe njoɓdi timmundi
  53,42,e wonnde ko ka Joomi maa woni haattirde nden
  53,43,e wonnde ko Kanko woni Weltinoowo Wullina
  53,44,ko Kanko kadi woni Warooro Wuurnita
  53,45,"e wonnde O tagii resindirayɗi ɗin ɗiɗi : gorel e deyel"
  53,46,immorde e toɓɓere maniiyu si rufaama
  53,47,e wonnde ko Kanko woodani tagitugol ɗimmun
  53,48,e wonnde ko Kanko woni alɗinɗo e okkɗuɗo
  53,49,e wonnde ko Kanko woni Jeyɗo hoodere Si'ira nden
  53,50,e wonnde ko Kanko halki Aadi'en adinooɓe
  53,51,"e Samuuda'en, O heddinaano hay e gooto"
  53,52,"Ko non kadi yimɓe Nuuhu ɓen ko adii[ɓe], pellet, ɓen laatino ɓurɓe tooñude e bewde"
  53,53,e yimɓe fitaare ɓen (ɓe) O waylitunoo
  53,54,O hippiri ɗe kon ko O hippiri
  53,55,Ko honɗum e neemaaji Joomi ma ɗin sikkitotoɗaa
  53,56,Awa oo ko jertinoowo jeyaaɗo e jertinooɓe adinooɓe
  53,57,Darngal ngal non ɓadike
  53,58,"Duñoowo ngal ko woori Allah, alaa"
  53,59,"E ko ndee yewtere [Alqur'aana] haawetoɗon"
  53,60,"Hiɗon jala, on wullataa"
  53,61,Hara ko on welsindiiɓe
  53,62,"Koni sujjanee Allah, rewon [Mo]"
  54,1,"Darngal ngal ɓadike, lewru ndun kadi seekike"
  54,2,"Si ɓe yi'ii maande, ɓe ɗuurnoo ɓe wi'a: \"Ko mbilewu jokkondirngu"
  54,3,"Ɓe fenni, ɓe jokki mbeleeɗe maɓɓe. Hara le huunde kala no mari ñiiɓirde"
  54,4,"Gomɗii kumpite arii e maɓɓe, ɗe haɗitorɗum woni e mun"
  54,5,"[Ɗum] ko ñeñƴal yottiingal. Kono jertingol ngol nafaali"
  54,6,Selu ɓe. Ñalnde noddoowo on noddoyta e huunde añiniinde
  54,7,"jaasuɓe ndaarɗe, hiɓe yaltira e genaale ɗen wano kanuuji caratooɗi"
  54,8,"heñaniiɓe noddoowo on. Heeferɓe ɓen wi'a: \"Ndee ko ñalaande sattunde"
  54,9,"Ado maɓɓe, yimɓe nuuhu ɓen yedduno. Ɓe fenni jeyaaɗo Amen on, ɓe wi'i : \"Ko jinnaaɗo!\", o kammbanaa"
  54,10,"O torii Joomi makko, wonnde : \"Min on ko mi foolaaɗo, faabo [lam]"
  54,11,"Men udditiri dammbuɗe kammu ngun, ndiyam wanncoojam"
  54,12,Men fuccitiri leydi ndin ɓulli. Ndiye ɗen fottiri e yamiroore hoddiranoonde
  54,13,"Men roondori mo e [laana] lesaaka marka alluwe e peŋe"
  54,14,"hika dogira e ndenka Amen. Ɗum ko njoɓdi [Nuuhu] fennanooɗo on. @Corrected"
  54,15,"Gomɗii Men accirii [kon ko Men waɗi ɓe] tasakuyee. Taw si woodi waajitorayɗo"
  54,16,Taskii ko honno lepte Am e jertinol (Am) wa'unoo
  54,17,Gomɗii Men newinirii Alqur'aanare nden waajitorgol. Hara wooday waajitorɗo
  54,18,Aadi'en fennuno. Taskee ko honno lepte Am e jertinol (Am) wa'unoo
  54,19,"Men wurtu e maɓɓe henndu sattundu, e ñalaande hiitaande, duumiinde"
  54,20,"hindu wippitira yimɓe ɓen, wa si tawii ko ɓe daƴƴe tamaro irtaaɗe"
  54,21,Taskee ko honno lepte Am ɗen e jertinol (Am) ngol wa'unoo
  54,22,Gomɗii Men newinirii Alqur'aanare nden sabu waajitorgol. Hara wooday waajitorɗo
  54,23,Samuuda'en fennuno waaju ngun
  54,24,"ɓe wi'i: \"Kere ko neɗɗo gooto e amen woni ko men jokkata? Haray men wonii ontuma e nder majjere e tamperere"
  54,25,"Hara ko e makko jantoore nden werlaa hakkunde amen? Si ko woni, ko fenoowo nii, townitiiɗo"
  54,26,"Aray ɓe annda (Ñalnde) Janngo, ko hommbo woni fenoowo townitiiɗo on"
  54,27,"Ko Men wurtirooɓe ngelooba ndewa mbam, jarribagol ɓe. Aynitu ɓe, muññoɗaa"
  54,28,"Humpitu ɓe wonnde ndiyam ɗam ko sennndaaɗam hakkunde maɓɓe [e ngelooba mbam]; kala yaray geɓal mun"
  54,29,"Ɓe noddi wonndiiɗo maɓɓe, o jonni [kaafa kan], o sodi [mba]"
  54,30,Teskii ko honno lepte Am ɗen e jertinol (Am) ngol wa'unoo
  54,31,"Ko haacaango wooturu tun Men wurti e maɓɓe, ɓe wa'i wa ledde yooruɗe muncaaɗe"
  54,32,Gomɗii Men newinirii Alqur'aanare nden waajitorgol. Hara wooday waajitorɗo
  54,33,Yimɓe Luutu ɓen fennuno jertine ɗen
  54,34,"Men wurtuno henndu kaaƴe e maɓɓe, si wanaa e ɓeynguure Luutu nden, Men daɗndirno ɓen ka wenndo"
  54,35,"moƴƴere immorde e Amen. Ko non Men yoɓitirta kala yettuɗo [neema Allah on]"
  54,36,Gomɗii le o jertinirno ɓe nanngal Amen cattungal ngal. Kono ɓe sikkitii jertinol ngol
  54,37,"Gomɗii ɓe ɗaɓɓirno mo [bonidugol e hoɗɓe makko ɓen]. Men mehi gite maɓɓe ɗen. \"Meeɗee lepte ɗen e jertinol Am ngol"
  54,38,"Gomɗii ko bimmbi law, woni ko lepte duumiiɗe dawirani ɓe"
  54,39,Meeɗee lepte e jertinol Am
  54,40,Gomɗii Men newinirii Alqur'aanare nden waajitorgol. Hara wooday waajitorɗo
  54,41,Gomɗii jertinaango ngon arii e yimɓe Fir'awna ɓen
  54,42,"Ɓe fenni Aayeeje Amen ɗen fow. Men nanngiri ɓe, nanngal Fooluɗo Hattanɗo"
  54,43,Kere ko heeferɓe mon ɓen ɓuri ɓeya moƴƴude? Kaa ko daɗugol woodani on ka Ɗeri
  54,44,"Kaa hara ɓe wi'ay : \"Menen ko men dental wallindirooɓe"
  54,45,"Aray nde dental [maɓɓe] ngal foolee, ɓe runntina ɓabbe maɓɓe"
  54,46,"Wurin ko Darngal ngal woni kammbaa maɓɓe on, Ko Darngal non ɓuri mawnude e haaɗude"
  54,47,"Pellet, bomɓe ɓen wonii e majjere e ooyunge"
  54,48,"Ñalnde ɓe daasiroytee geece maɓɓe ɗen ka nder Yiite, (ɓe wi'anee): \"Meeɗee meemugol Saqara"
  54,49,Menen Men tagir huunde kala e eɓɓoore
  54,50,"Yamiroore Amen wonaali, si wanaa [konngol] gootol pet, [yaawira] wa hinƴaango yiitere"
  54,51,Gomɗii Men halkiino yeradiiɓe mon. Hara wooday waajitorayɗo
  54,52,Kala huunde nde ɓe golli no ka nder ɗeri
  54,53,"kala kadi toksum e mawnukum, ko winndaaɗum"
  54,54,"Pellet, gomɗuɓe ɓen wonii e Aljannaaji e canɗi"
  54,55,"e toolorde goonga, ka Laamɗo Hattanɗo"
  55,1,Jom Hinaraŋke On
  55,2,O anndinii Alqur'aana
  55,3,O tagi neɗɗaŋke
  55,4,O anndini mo ɓanngingol
  55,5,"Naange ngen e lewru ndun [hino dogira] limoore"
  55,6,"koode ɗen kadi e leɗɗe ɗen, hino sujjude"
  55,7,"Kammu ngun, O toownu ngu. O waɗi nunɗal ngal"
  55,8,fii wata on bewu ka peesirɗe
  55,9,Ñinniron etugol ngol no nunɗiri. Wata on ɗuytu peesirɗe ɗen
  55,10,"Leydi ndin, O waɗanndi tagoore nden"
  55,11,"muuyanteeɗi hino e mayri, e leɗɗe tamaro marɗe poƴƴi"
  55,12,"e gabbe marɗe ñaande, e uurngol"
  55,13,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin woni ko fennoton
  55,14,"O tagiri neɗɗo on immorde e loopal, wa'ungal wa ko juɗaa"
  55,15,"O tagiri jinnaaji ɗin, immorde e lew lewndu yiite laaɓuki"
  55,16,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,17,Jeyɗo fuɗirɗe ɗen ɗiɗi Jeyi kadi mutirɗe ɗen ɗiɗi
  55,18,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,19,"O Tuppindiri maaje ɗen ɗiɗi, hiɗe fotta"
  55,20,"heedo hino hakkunde majje, ɗe jillondirtaa"
  55,21,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,22,"Hino yalta e ɗen [maaje] ɗiɗi: kaŋŋe \"Lu'lu'u\" e \"Marjaan"
  55,23,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,24,"Ko Kanko woodani dogooje lesaaɗe ka nder maayo, wa'uɗe wa pelle"
  55,25,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,26,Kala ko woni e hoore mayri ko ko re'ata
  55,27,"heddoo Jaati Joomi maa Kin, Jom mawngu e teddungal. @Corrected"
  55,28,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,29,"Ɓen wonɓe ka kammuuli e ka leydi hino naamnoo Mo. Ñalnde woo, Himo e fiyaaku"
  55,30,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,31,"Aray nde Men faandii hasbude on, onon yo tedda ko'e en ɗiɗo"
  55,32,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,33,"Ko onon yo dental jinna e yimɓe ! Si on hattanii wuɗɗirgol ka seraaji kammuuli e ka leydi, haray wuɗɗee. On wuɗɗirtaa si wanaa e doole"
  55,34,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,35,"Hino wurtee e mon - [onon jinna e yimɓe] - ɗemngal yiite e curki [maa sila taayuɗo], on faabondirtaa"
  55,36,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,37,"Si wonii kammu ngun seekike, ngu wojjirii wa piindi hono pentiir boɗe"
  55,38,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,39,"Nden ñalnde, wanaa neɗɗo maa jinne woni ko lanmditetee fii junuubi mun"
  55,40,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,41,Bomɓe ɓen hino annditiree maandeeji maɓɓe ɗin. Ɓe nanngiroyee ka njubuuji-tin tinɗi- e ka koyɗe
  55,42,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin woni ko fennoton
  55,43,Ko ngee woni Jahannama nge bomɓe ɓen fennaynoo fii mun
  55,44,Hiɓe wanngoo hakkunde magge e fatayɗam hattuɗam wulde
  55,45,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,46,"Hino woodani kala hulɗo daragol yeeso Joomi mun, aljannaaji ɗiɗi"
  55,47,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,48,marɗe calɗi ɗiɗi dukke
  55,49,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,50,"Ɓulli ɗiɗi hino e nder majji, ilayɗi. @Corrected"
  55,51,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,52,"Hino e nder majji kala muuyanteeɗi ɗin, noone ɗiɗi"
  55,53,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,54,"Hara ko ɓe soɓɓindiiɓe e ndaɗɗule tekkirɗe nder, dimɗe majje ɗen ɗiɗi ko ɓadiiɗe"
  55,55,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,56,"(Rewɓe) raɓɓiɗa ndaarɗeɓe hino toon, ɓe neɗɗo memaali ado maɓɓe wanaa kadi jinna"
  55,57,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,58,"[Labiraaɓe] wa kaŋŋe yaaquutu e marjaan"
  55,59,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,60,"Hara njoɓdi moƴƴere no woodi, si wanaa moƴƴere"
  55,61,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,62,"Hino gaanin ɗin ɗiɗi, aljannaaji ɗiɗi kadi"
  55,63,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,64,hecciɗuɗi ɗiɗi
  55,65,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,66,"Ɓulli ɗiɗi hino e nder majji, ɓulayɗi"
  55,67,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,68,"Hino e majji : muuyanteeɗi, e leɗɗe tamaro e rummaana"
  55,69,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,70,"Hino e ɗin ɗiɗi : rewɓe suɓaaɓe labaaɓe"
  55,71,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,72,"huurul'ayniiɓe, soomaaɓe e tillisooji"
  55,73,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,74,"neɗɗo memaali ɓen ado maɓɓe, wanaa kadi jinna"
  55,75,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,76,"Ko ɓe soɓɓindotooɓe e hoore ngawluuji haakooji, e ndaɗɗule abqari labaaɗe"
  55,77,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,78,"Barkinii Innde Joomi maa nden, Jom Mawngu e Teddungal"
  56,1,Si darotoongal ngal darike
  56,2,alanaa daragol maggal ngol fennoowo
  56,3,"Hoyfinɗinayngal (yedduɓe), ɓamtayngal (gomɗimɓe)"
  56,4,Si leydi ndin dilliniraama dillannde
  56,5,pelle ɗen munciroyee muncannde
  56,6,ɗe wonta collaari ruuynayndi
  56,7,wattinon nooneeji tati
  56,8,Ko wontirooɓe ñaamo ɓen - iskin ɓen yimɓe ñaamo
  56,9,"e wontirooɓe nano ɓen, bis e ɓen yimɓe nano"
  56,10,"Ko adondiraynooɓe ɓen (e moƴƴere ka aduna), adoytee (naadeede Aljanna)"
  56,11,Ko ɓen woni badnitaaɓe ɓen
  56,12,ka Aljannaaji neeminiiɗi
  56,13,"dental jeyaangal e [mofte] adinooɓe ɓen"
  56,14,"e seeɗaaɓe jeyaaɓe e [mofte] sakkitiiɓe ɓen"
  56,15,"hiɓe e hoore danɗe yuɓɓiraaɗe [kaŋŋe]"
  56,16,"hara hiɓe soɓɓindii e majje, fewtondirɓe"
  56,17,Sukaaɓe duuminaaɓe hino wanngoo hakkunde maɓɓe
  56,18,"wonndude e ñedduɗe, e cataloy, e koroy e [hebbiniraakoy] beere ilaynde"
  56,19,"ɓe muusetaake ko*e nder ton, ɓe siwritaa"
  56,20,e muuyanteeɗi ɗi ɓe suɓotoo
  56,21,e teewu colli ngu ɓe tuuyatee
  56,22,e huurul'ayniiɓe -yaaja gite en
  56,23,nannduɓe e kaŋŋe lu'lu'u maraaɗe
  56,24,njoɓdi ko ɓe gollaynoo kon
  56,25,"Ɓe nanataa nder ton haala meere, wanaa ko bakkondiŋta"
  56,26,"si wanaa wi'aneede : \"Salaaman! Salaaman!\" [Saɗi mon! saɗi mon]"
  56,27,"E wontirooɓe ñaamo ɓen, ko woni ɓen yimɓe ñaamo"
  56,28,"[Ɓe wonay] e leɗɗe jaaɓe newɗuɗe"
  56,29,e banaanaje fawandirɗe
  56,30,e ɗowdi duumiindi
  56,31,e ndiyam juurayɗam
  56,32,e ɓiɗɓe leɗɗe ɗuuɗuɗe
  56,33,ɗe taƴondirtaa ɗe haɗetaake
  56,34,e danɗe ɓamtaaɗe
  56,35,Ko Menen tagi fuɗɗi ɓe
  56,36,Men waɗi ɓe curbaaɓe-boomi
  56,37,"yiɗuɓe worɓe mun, goreeɓe"
  56,38,"[Men marani ɓe] yimɓe ñaamo ɓen"
  56,39,"Dental jeyaaɓe e [mofte] adinooɓe ɓen"
  56,40,"e seeɗaaɓe jeyaaɓe e [mofte] sakkitiiɓe ɓen"
  56,41,E wontirooɓe nano ɓen. Ko homɓe woni ɓen yimɓe nano
  56,42,"[Ɓen] no e nguleendi e fatayɗam"
  56,43,e ɗowdi curki ɓawluki
  56,44,"wonaa ɓuuɓundi, wanaa teddundi"
  56,45,"Ado ɗum, hari ko ɓe neeminaaɓe"
  56,46,ɓe laatino hiɓe deppitoo e bakkaat mawɗi ɗin
  56,47,"hiɓe wi'aynoo: \"Enee, si men maayii, men wontii mbullaari e ƴi'e, hara ko men immintinoyteeɓe"
  56,48,hay baabiraaɓe amen adinooɓe ɓen
  56,49,"Maaku : \"Pellet, aramɓe e sakkitiiɓe"
  56,50,ko mooɓoyteeɓe e ñalaande anndaande waqutu mun
  56,51,"refti pellet, onon ɓee majjuɓe fennuɓe [ummital]"
  56,52,"ko on nyaamoyayɓe e leggal \"Zaqquumi\" ngal"
  56,53,ngal hebbiniroyton deedi
  56,54,yariron ngal kadi fatayɗam
  56,55,yariron wa yarugol ngelooba ɗomɗaamba
  56,56,Ko ɗum woni ko ɓe kottiigu !u! en ñalnde njoɓdi diina
  56,57,"Ko Menen woni ko tagi on. Haɗi goonginon [Men immintinay on]"
  56,58,On yi'ii on maniiyu mo rufoton
  56,59,"Ko onon tagata mo? Kaa ko Menen woni tagooɓe [ɗum]"
  56,60,Ko Menen hoddiri maayde nden hakkunde mon. Men wonaali adateeɓe
  56,61,"e wattitugol yeruuɓe mon, Men fuɗɗira on e ko on anndah"
  56,62,Gomɗii hiɗon anndi tageede aranun ɗum. Ko haɗi waajitoɗon
  56,63,On yi'ii kon ko remoton
  56,64,Ko onon fuɗinta ɗum? Kaa ko Menen woni fuɗinooɓe ɓen
  56,65,"Si Men haajuno, pellet, Men waɗayno ndu foron. Wattinon hiɗon haawoo [wi'a]"
  56,66,Menen ko men lepteteeɓe perte ko min nafqi ko
  56,67,wurin ko men haɗaaɓe
  56,68,On yi'ii ndiyam ɗam yaroton ɗam
  56,69,"E ko onon jippiniri ɗam ka duule? Kaa ko Menen jippini [ɗam]"
  56,70,"Si Men haajuno, Men waɗayno ɗam kaaɗɗam. Ko haɗi yetton [Allah]"
  56,71,On yi'ii yiite nge huɓɓoton ngen
  56,72,"E ko onon woodini waɗi leɗɗe mum? Kaa ko Menen woodini [ɗe]"
  56,73,"Men waɗir ngen [yiite] waaju, e nafitor nge setotooɓe"
  56,74,"Subbunhinor innde Joomi maa, Mawɗo On"
  56,75,Mi woondirii mutirɗe koode ɗen
  56,76,"Pellet, ɗum ko woondoore mawnde, si hiɗon anndunoo"
  56,77,Pellet ndee ko Alqur'aanaare konde teddunde
  56,78,wonnde e deftere reenaande
  56,79,meemataa nden si wanaa laɓɓinaaɓe ɓen
  56,80,ko jippiniraande ka Jeyɗo Winndere nden
  56,81,E ko ndee yewtere wonki ko pennoton onon
  56,82,"Hiɗon waɗa arsike mon (toɓo ngon) ko on fennooɓe [arsikuɗo On]"
  56,83,Ko haɗata nde wonkii yottii ka lookoƴere
  56,84,hara onon hiɗon ndaara ontuma
  56,85,"hara non ko Menen ɓuri on ɓadaade mo, kono on yi'ataa"
  56,86,"Ko haɗata on, si tawiino hara on warjetaake"
  56,87,"rutton kin [wonkii], si tawii ko on goonguɓe"
  56,88,Si tawii on ko jeyaaɗo e ɓattinaaɓe ɓen
  56,89,"haray ko fowtere, e moƴƴere, e Aljannaaji neema (woodani mo)"
  56,90,Si tawii kadi ko jeyaaɗo e yimɓe ñaamo ɓen
  56,91,"haray [o jaɓɓoroyte] : \"Kisal maa\" e ɓaŋge yimɓe ñaamo ɓen"
  56,92,Si tawii non ko jeyanooɗo e fennuɓe majjuɓe ɓen
  56,93,haray hoɗtorde makko on ko fatayɗam
  56,94,e sumeede Jahiimi
  56,95,"Pellet, ko ɗum woni goonga yananaaɗo on"
  56,96,"Subbunhinor innde Joomi maa, Mawɗo On"
  57,1,"Kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi seninii Allah. Ko Kanko woni Fooluɗo, Ñeeño On"
  57,2,"Ko Kanko heeranii laamu kammuuli ɗin e leydi ndin. Himo wuurna Himo wara, Kanko ko O hattanɗo kala huunde"
  57,3,"Ko Kanko woni Arano e Sakkitiiɗo, Feeñuɗo e Wirniiɗo, Kanko ko O annduɗo kala huunde"
  57,4,"Ko Kanko tagi kammuuli ɗin e leydi ndin nder balɗe jeegoo, refti O fotondiri ka dow \"Arsi\"; Himo anndi ko mutata kon ka leydi, e ko ƴawata e mayri, e ko jipporta ka kammu e ko ƴawata e maggu. Himo wonndi e mon kala ka wonɗon. Allah no reeni ko golloton kon. @Corrected"
  57,5,Ko Kanko heeranii laamu kammuuli ɗin e leydi ndin. Ko ka Allah fiyakuuji ɗin ruttirtee
  57,6,"Himo naadia jemma on e nder ñalorma on, O naadira ñalorma on kadi e nder jemma on. Kanko ko O annduɗo ko woni e nder ɓerɗe"
  57,7,"Gomɗinee Allah e Nulaaɗo Makko on, nafqon kon ko O waɗiri on lomtinaaɓe e mun. Gomɗimɓe ɓen e mon, ɓe nafqi [jawle maɓɓe ɗen], hino woodani ɓen njoɓdi mawnundi"
  57,8,"E ko heɓi on, on gomɗintaa Allah? E hino Nulaaɗo on hino nodda on e gomɗingol Joomi mon. Gomɗii [Allah] ƴettii e mon ahadi, si on laatike gomɗimɓe"
  57,9,"Ko Kanko jippinta e jeyaaɗo Makko on Aayeeje ɓannguɗe, fii no o yaltinira on e niɓe faade e ndaygu. Pellet, Allah ko Yuminoowo on, Hinnotooɗo"
  57,10,"E ko heɓi on, on sakkotaako fii laawol Allah ngol, e hino le ko Allah woodani ronugol kammuuli ɗin e leydi ndin? Fotataa e mon, ɓen sakkinooɓe ado uddital ngal ɓe haɓidaa; ko ɓen ɓuri mawnude darja e dii ɓen sakkiiɓe ɓaawo ɗum ɓe haɓidaa. Ɓe fow maɓɓe non, Allah fodii ɓe moƴƴere. Allah no humpitii ko golloton kon"
  57,11,"Ko hommbo ñawlirta Allah ñamaande labaande, O sowana mo nde, hara no woodani mo njoɓdi teddundi"
  57,12,"Ñalnde yi'oytaa gomɗimɓe worɓe ɓen e gomɗimɓe rewɓe ɓen, hara annoora maɓɓe yaara yeeso maɓɓe e ñaamo maɓɓe (ɓe wi'anee): \"Weltaare mon hannde ko Aljannaaji, ɗi canɗi ilata senngo ley mun, ko on duumotooɓe nder ton\". Ko ɗum woni malal mawngal ngal"
  57,13,"Ñalnde naafiqiiɓe worɓe ɓen e naafiqiiɓe rewɓe ɓen wi'anoyta gomɗimɓe ɓen: \"Habbee men, men jalbinora annoora mon on\". Ɓe wi'anee : \"Yiltoree ɓaawo mon, ɗaɓɓoyon annoora\". Heedo waɗee hakkunde maɓɓe, ngo damal ngal yurmeende woni e nder mun, ɓaawo maggal noon, ko lepte woni e bannge mun"
  57,14,"Hiɓe nodda ɓe : \"E men wondaano e mon?\" Ɓe wi'a : \"Ko non woniri. Ko woni tun, on fitinno ko'e mon, habbitaniɗon [gomɗimɓe ɓen bone], sikkitiɗon, yelaaji hodi on haa yamiroore Allah nden ari. Hodoowo on hodi on e moƴƴere Allah nden"
  57,15,"Hannde on, on jaɓantaake soktorɗum wanaa e ɓen yedduɓe. Depporde mon nden ko ka Yiite : ko ngen woni ko hannduɗon. Nge bonii ruttorde"
  57,16,"E yontaani gomɗimɓe ɓen nde ɓerɗe maɓɓe ɗen deeƴirta jantoore Allah nden e kon ko jippii immorde e goonga? Hara ɓe wa'aali wa ɓen okkanooɓe Defte ɓen ko adii, dumunna on juutani ɓen, ɓerɗe maɓɓe ɗen yoori, ko ɗuuɗunoo e maɓɓe kon ko faasiqiiɓe"
  57,17,"Anndee pellet, Allah wuurnitay leydi ndin ɓaawo ndi yoorii. Gomɗii Men ɓannginiranii on Aayeeje ɗen, fii no haqqiliron"
  57,18,"Pellet, sakkotooɓe (jawle mun ɓen) ka worɓe e ka rewɓe ɓe ñawli Allah ñamaande labaande, ɓe sowanoyte (mbarjaari) hara no woodani ɓe njoɓdi mawndi"
  57,19,"Ɓen gomɗimɓe Allah e Nulaaɗo Makko on, ko ɓen woni goongiyaŋke en. Sahodinɓe ɓen ka Joomi mun, hino woodani ɓen njoɓdi maɓɓe e annoora maɓɓe. Ɓen non yedduɓe ɓe fenni Aayeeje Amen ɗen, ko ɓen woni yimɓe Jahiimi ngen"
  57,20,"Anndee wonnde nguurndam aduna ɗam ko fijindaaru, e mbeleeɗe, e cuɗaari, e ɓurondiro hakkunde mon e jawle e ɓiɗɓe. Wano toɓo haawnungo remooɓe ɓen puɗi mun, refti ngo yoora, yi'aa hingo soyɗi; refti ngo wonta munciiɗum. Hino ka laakara, lette saɗtuɗe, e yaafuyee immorde e Allah e yarluyee. Nguurndam aduna ɗam wonaali, si wanaa dakammehoy hodo"
  57,21,"Adondiree e (golle) yaafaawuya ka Joomi mon, e Aljanna mo yaajeendi mun wa'i yaajeendi kammu ngun e leydi ndin, on maranaama ɓen gomɗimɓe Allah e Nulaaɓe Makko ɓen. Ɗum ko ɓural Allah ngal O okkata on mo O muuyani. Allah ko Jom ɓural mawnungal"
  57,22,"Bone woo heɓataa [on] e leydi ndin maa e pittaali mon ɗin, si wanaa ɗum woniino e deftere ado Men tagude ndee [tagoore]. Pellet, ɗum ko ko newanii Allah"
  57,23,"Ko fii wata on suno e ko laawii on kon, wanaa kadi weltorgol ko O okki on kon. Allah yiɗaa kala ñaaƴoowo, mantiiɗo"
  57,24,"Ɓen wuddooɓe ɓe yamira yimɓe ɓen nguddam... kala ɗuurniiɗo, pellet, Allah kan ko Galo, Yettiniiɗo"
  57,25,"Gomɗii Men nulirii Nulaaɓe Amen ɓen ɓanngannduyeeji, Men jippindinani ɓe Defte e sariyaare, fii no yimɓe ɓen ñiiɓira e nunɗal. Men jippini kadi njamndi ndin, ndi doole tiiɗuɗe woni e mun e nafooje wonannde yimɓe ɓen, e no Allah feññinira ɓen wallooɓe Mo e Nulaaɗo Makko on ka wirnii. Pellet, Allah ko Jom cemmbe, Fooluɗo. @Corrected"
  57,26,"Gomɗii Men nulii Nuuhu e Ibraahiima, Men waɗi e geyngol maɓɓe ngol Annabaaku e Defte. Hino e maɓɓe feewuɓe, ko ɗuuɗi kon e maɓɓe ko faasiqiiɓe"
  57,27,"Refti Men jokkindini e batteeji maɓɓe ɗin, Nulaaɓe Amen [goo], Men jokkintiniri [ɓe] Iisaa geɗal Maryama on, Men okki mo Linjiila, Men waɗi e ɓerɗe jokkuɓe mo ɓen : yurmeende e giggol. Labbeyaagal ngal ɓe sinci ngal, Menen Men waɗɗinaa ngal e maɓɓe. [Men lamndaaki] si wanaa ɗaɓɓugol welayee Allah. Kono ɓe ayniraali ɗum no haani aynireede. Men okki njoɓdi gomɗimɓe ɓen e maɓɓe. Ko ɗuuɗunoo kon e maɓɓe ko faasiqiiɓe"
  57,28,"Ko onon yo gomɗimɓe! Hulee Allah, gomɗinon Nulaaɗo Makko on; O yeɗay on geɗe ɗiɗi e mbarjaari Makko ndin, O waɗana on annoora mo ndayginorton, O haforana on. Pellet, Allah ko Haforoowo, Hinnotooɗo"
  57,29,"Fii no yimɓe Defte ɓen anndira wonnde ɓe hattanaa hay huunde e ɓural Allah ngal, e wonnde ɓural ngal ko e juuɗe Allah woni; Himo yeɗa ngal mo O muuyani. Pellet, Allah ko Jom ɓural mawngal"
  58,1,Ko goonga Alla nani konngol oon duttondiroowo e ma haala ko faati e jom galle makko hombo wullito faade e Alla; Alla na nana yeewtere mon nde pellet Alla ko nanoowo ji*oowo
  58,2,"ɓeen nanndinooɓe suddiiɓe mum en e yummiraaɓe maɓɓe, ɓeen ɓe ngonah yummiraaɓe maɓɓƴe, woni yummiraaɓe mum en ko ɓeen jibinɓe ɓe pellet hoɓe haala pankare e fenaande e pellet Alla ko jaafatooɗo jarlotooɗo bakkatuuji"
  58,3,"ɓeen nanndinooɓe rewɓe mum en refti ɓe ndutto ko ɓe mbiino ko yoɓe ndimɗin daande ko adi ndeɓe memandirta ko ɗum woni ko mbaajete ɗon ko, Alla na humpati ko ngollaton ko"
  58,4,"Kala mbo dañaani yo o hoor lebbi ɗiɗi dewandirɗi ko adii ndeɓe mandirta kala mbo hattanaani yo o ñammin miskineeɓe capanɗe njeegom, ɗuum ko ngam ngoonɗinon Alla e nelaaɗo makko ko ɗuum woni keerol Alla woodanii heeferɓe lepte cattuɗe"
  58,5,"Pellet ɓeen luundotooɓe Alla e Nelaaɗo Makko ɓe hoynaama hono no adiiɓe ɓe koynirano, Min tellinii aayeeje peeñɗe, woodani heeferɓe lepte koynooje"
  58,6,"Ñande O ummini ɓe kamɗe fof O holla ɓe koɓe golluno ko, O tonngii ɗuum ɓe njejji ɗum Alla na seedii kala huunde"
  58,7,"Mbela a anndah wonde Alla na anndi ko woni e nder kammuuli e ko woni e nder leydi, gunndo wonatah hakkunde tata si wonah O nayɓitaɓe ngo wonatah hakkunde noyo si wonah O wona jeegoɓo ngo wonatah ko jaasi ɗuum si wonah O wonda e mum en toɓe mbaawi wonde fof, refti O habraɓe ko ɓe golli ñande darnga, pellet Alla na anndi kala huunde"
  58,8,"Mbela a yiyaani ɓeen haɗaaɓe ndeeyu refti ɓe nduttoo koɓe kada ko ɓe ndeeyandira e bakkatuuji e añanaagal e woopde nelaaɗo, siɓi ngarii e ma ɓe calmanir ma na Alla salminiraani ma nih ɓe wiya e pittaali mum en ko haɗi Alla leptira min ko min kaalata ko, yoniiɓe jahannama hoɓe naatne heen bonii wattannde"
  58,9,"Eehey mon gooɗinɓe si on ndeeydii e nelaaɗo wotee ndeeyde e makko e bakkaat e añanaagal e woopde nelaaɗo, ndeeydee e ɗiggere e kulol Alla Mbo mooɓoyteɗon to Makko"
  58,10,"Pellet gunndo ko e seytaane ngam o sunina ɓeen goonɗinɓe o lorotaaɓe hay ndiga si wonah e sakkitoore Alla, e dow Alla woni ko goonɗiɓe wakkilto"
  58,11,"Eehey mon goonɗinɓe si on wiyaama yaacne e jolle yaacne Alla yaajnana mon, si on wiyaama umme, ummɗon Alla ɓamta ɓeen goonɗin ɓe e mon e joman en ganndal darajaaji, Alla na humpatii ko golloton ko"
  58,12,"Eehey mon goonɗinɓe si on ndeeydii e nelaaɗo tottire e ndeeyu mon sadak, ko ɗuum ɓuri moƴƴude e mon ko ɗuum ɓuri laaɓde, si on keɓaani Alla de ko jaafatooɗo jurmotooɗo"
  58,13,"Mbela on kul tottirde sadaka saanga ndeeydaton e nelaaɗo, si on tottiraani Alla jaɓani on tuubuubuya, ndarnee juulde toottiron askal ɗoftoɗon Alla e nelaaɗo makko, Alla na humpatii ko golloton ko"
  58,14,"Mbela a yi*aani ɓeen heedninɓe aade en ɓe Alla tikkani ɓe njeyaaka e mon ɓe njeyaako e maɓɓe, hoɓe ngoondira penaale te hoɓe nganndi"
  58,15,Alla heblaniiɓe lepte cattuɗe pellet bonii koɓe golluno ko
  58,16,"ɓe nanngarii goondooje mum en ɗe heedo, ɓe palii laawol Alla ngol, woodaniiɓe lepte koynooje"
  58,17,"Pellet, ɓeen yedduɓe, jawle maɓɓe ɗen e ɓiɗɓe maɓɓe ɓen duncantaaɓe e lepte Alla ɗen hay huunde. Ko ɓeen ɗon woni yimɓe yiite ɓen, kamɓe ko ɓe luttooɓe ton"
  58,18,"Ñande Alla umminiɓe kamɓe fof, ɓe ngoondana Mbo hono noɓe woondaranta mon nih, hoɓe sikka won koɓe ngoni e dow mum, ɓe tigi ngoni fenooɓe ɓe"
  58,19,"Seytaane tehriiɓe o yejjitini ɓe jantaade Alla ko ɓee tigi ngoni fedde seytaane, pellet ko fedde seytaane woni pertuɓe"
  58,20,"ɓeen haɓatooɓe Alla e nelaaɗo Makko,ko ɓeen ɓuri hoyde"
  58,21,"Alla ñaawi ma Mi fool Miin e nelaaɓe am, pellet Alla ko cemmbuɗo tedduɗo"
  58,22,"A heɓatah yimɓe goonɗinɓe e ñalawma cakkatiiɗo na njiɗandira e luundiiɓe Alla e nelaaɗo makko haysi ɓe ngonii baabiraaɓe mum en wolla ɓiɓɓe wolla musiɓɓe, wolla gorol mum en, ko ɓe ɓerɗe mum en mbinnda iimaan O semmbiniɓe e ruuhu ummade e Makko, O naatnaɓe aljannaaji na dogo ley majji caatli ɓe duumo toon haa pooma, Alla weleeɓe ɓe mbele Alla, ko ɓeen ngoni fedde Alla, ko fedde Alla tigi woni malaaɓe. @Corrected"
  59,1,"Kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi seninii Allah. Ko Kanko woni Fooluɗo, Ñeeño On"
  59,2,"Ko kanko yaltini ɓeen heefeeeɓe jom en defte en e galleeji mum en e mooɓdu adanuru ndu, on cikkaana maɓe njaltu, ɓe cikki galli mum en ɗi ndeenatɓe e Alla, O ardiɓe ɗoɓe cikkaana, O werlii e ɓerɗe mum en kulol, hoɓe njirbinira galleeji maɓɓe juuɗe mum en e juuɗe goonɗinɓe, teskee onon joman en hakkillaaji"
  59,3,Si Alla farlaana e mum en yaltineede ma O leptuɓe e aduna woodanaɓe lepte yiite
  59,4,"Ɗum, ko fii kamɓe ɓe lunndike Alla e Nulaaɗo Makko on. \"Kala non lunndiiɗo Alla e Nulaaɗo Makko on, pellet, Alla ko Caɗtuɗo lepte"
  59,5,"Kala ko taƴɗon e tamaroowi wolla accuɗonki hoki dari e pooɓe makki, ko e yamiroore Alla ngam O hoyna faasiqeeɓe"
  59,6,"Ko Alla rutti faade e nelaaɗo Makko ummaade e mum en, on keñaraaki e mum pucci wolla geloobi, kono Alla na wuurta nelaaɓe makko e dow mbo o wela, Alla na hattani kala huunde"
  59,7,"Ko Alla neemini e nelaaɗo Mum e yimɓe gure dow, na woodani Alla e nelaaɗo makko e ɓadiiɓe nelaado e alyatitm en e miskineeɓe e ɓiy laawol ngam ɗum waasa yiilaade hakkunde alɗuɓe mon, ko nelaaɗo totti on ɓame ko o haɗi on ngacce, ndeene Alla, pellet Alla ko cattuɗo lepte"
  59,8,"Woodani waasɗe yaltinaaɓe galleeji mum en e jawɗeele mum en hoɓe ɗaɓɓa ɓural ummaade e Alla e weluya hoɓe mballa Alla e nelaaɗo makko, ko ɓeen de ngoni goonɗuɓe tigi"
  59,9,"E ɓeen telliiɓe e madiina e iimaan ko adii ɓe, hoɓe njiɗi oon perɗo faade e maɓɓe ɓe keɓatah e ɓerɗe mum en tikkere koɓe totta ko, hoɓe ɓurna e dow ko*e mum en haysi hoɓe wondi e baasal, kala mbo Alla reeni fittaandu mum e ɗawre, ko ɓeen de ngoni malaaɓe"
  59,10,"E ɓeen arɓe caggal mum en na mbi*a joomo amen yaafa amen minen e musiɓɓe amen adiiɓe amen e iimaan wotah waɗ e ɓerɗe amen cokotaagal wonande ɓeen goonɗinɓe,joomi amen ko Aan woni enɗiiɗo jurmotooɗo"
  59,11,"Mbela a yi*aani ɓeen naafaqinɓe wiiɓe musibbe mum en yedduɓe jeyaaɓe e yimɓe defte, si on yaltii pellet ma min yaltid e mon, min ɗototaako e dow mon hay gooto, si on kaɓaama ma min mballu mon Alla na seedo koɓe fenooɓe"
  59,12,Siɓe yaltinaama ɓe yaltidtah e mum en si ɓe kaɓaama ɓe wallataa ɓe siɓe walliiɓe maɓe runta refti ɓe walletaake
  59,13,"Ko onon ɓuri sattu kulo e ɓerɗe maɓɓe gaa nih e Alla, waɗi noon koɓe yimɓe ɓe paamatah"
  59,14,ɓe haɓatah e mon si wonah hoɓe e gure taartinaaɗe galli wolla caggal mahdeele bone maɓɓe hakkunde mum en na satti haɗa sikka koɓe gootum kono ɓerɗe maɓɓe na ceerti waɗi noon koɓe yimɓe ɓe kakkiltah
  59,15,Hona yeru ɓeen adiiɓe ɓe ko ɓadii ɓe meeɗi lepte fiyaaku mum en woodaniiɓe lepte cattuɗe
  59,16,"Ko hono seytaane nde wi*i neɗɗanke o yeddu, nde o yeddi o wi*i miin komi kisɗo e ma, miin mbeɗo huli Alla jom binnde O"
  59,17,"Laati batte mum en kanɓe ɗiɗa ko yiite saasooɓe toon, ɗuum ko njoɓdi tooñooɓe"
  59,18,"Eehey mon goonɗibe ndeente Alla, yo fittaandu ndaar kondu ardinani jannga kule Alla pellet Alla ko kumpatiiɗo ko ngolloton ko"
  59,19,"Wote ngone hono ɓeen yejjitɓe Alla, O yejjitini ɓe pittaali mum en ko ɓeen ngoni faasiqeeɓe"
  59,20,"Yimɓe yiite e yimɓe aljanna potatah, ko yimɓe aljanna ngoni foolɓe"
  59,21,Si min tellinna o quraana e dow hooseere ma a yiinde honde huli honde fetta ngam hulde Alla ɗi tinndi emin piyaniɗi yimɓe ko ngam ɓe miijo
  59,22,"Ko kanko woni deweteeɗo deweteeɗo e goonga alah si wonah kanko, ganndo ko wirni e ka wirnaaki kank woni jom yurmeende huftadinnde e yurmeende heeriinde"
  59,23,Ko kanko Alla mbo deweteeɗo e goonga alah si wonah kanko laamɗo ceniiɗo kisɗo goonɗiɗo kiilndiiɗo tedduɗo cemmbinɗo mawɗo senaare woodanii Alla e koɓe ndenndinta mbo ko
  59,24,"Ko kanko woni Alla tagɗo gootnuɗo mbaadinɗo tagu woodanii mbo inɗe ɓurɗe moƴƴude, woodanii mbo ko woni e nder kammuuji e leydi ko kanko woni pooloowo mbo hay gooto foolatah Ñeeñƴuɗo"
  60,1,"Eehey mon goonɗinɓe wote njaggire añɓe Mi e añɓe mon heetɓe hoɗon mberlo e mum en gilli te koɓe yedduɓe goongo garɗo o e mon, hoɓe njaltina nelaaɗo e onon sabu tan on ngoonɗanii Alla joomi mon, tawde on njalti sabu jihaadi e laawol Am e ɗaɓjude weluya am, hoɗon cuurtanaɓe kabaruuji juulɓe ngam ɓe mbele mon, Mbeɗa anndi ko cuuɗoton e ko ɓanngiɗon, kala e mon baɗɗo ɗuum o majji laawol peewngol"
  60,2,Siɓe peewnatiima e mon ɓe ngOnana mon añɓe ɓe mberta juuɗe maɓɓe e ɗemɗe mum en e mbaadi mbonndi ɓe njiɗiina nde ngonaton heefereeɓe
  60,3,Nafatah on enɗameeje mon wonah ɓiɓɓe mon ñande darnga O seernda hakkunde mon Alla na yi*a ko golloton ko
  60,4,"Woodanii on ñeemtinirde moƴƴere e Ibraahiima e ɓeen wonduɓe e mum nde ɓe mbi*i pellet ko min hisɓe e mon e ko ndewaton ko wonah Alla ko, min njeddii on feeñi hakkunde men ngañngu e tikkere haa pooma haa ngoonɗinon Alla gooto O, si wonah konngol Ibraahiima wonande baaba makko pellet ma mi yaafnano ma, mi alanaama hay huunde ka Alla, joomi amen min mbakkaliima e Ma ko e Ma min ndutti e ko e Ma woni wattande"
  60,5,"joomi amen wota waɗ min fitina wonande ɓeen yedduɓe, yaafa amen joomi amen pellet ko aan woni tedduɗo mbo fooletaake ñeeñɗuɗo"
  60,6,"Woodaniina mon e maɓɓe ñeemtanirgal moƴƴal wonande oon joortiiɗo e Alla e ñalngu laakara, oon ɗuurniiɗo noon Pellet Alla ko gala jettaaɗo"
  60,7,"Yaama nde Alla waɗata hakkunde mon e ɓeen ɓe ngañandirɗon gilli, Alla ko kattanɗo Alla ko kafroowo bakkatuuji jurmotooɗo"
  60,8,Alla haɗataa mon ɓeen ɓe kaɓaani e mon e diine ɓe njaltinaani mon e galleeji mon nde ɗiggantonɓe nuunɗon faade e maɓɓe pellet Alla ko jiɗɗo nuunɗuɓe
  60,9,"Kono Alla haɗata mon ko ɓeen haɓatooɓe mon e diine yaltinooɓe mon galleeji mon ɓe mballandiri e yaltinde mon, nde keetnaton ɓe kala baɗɗo ɓe keeda ko ɓeen ngoni tooñooɓe"
  60,10,"Eehey mon goonɗinɓe si goonɗinɓe rewɓe ngarii e mon njaribeeɓe Alla na anndi iimaan mum en, si on nganndii koɓe goonɗinɓe wotee ndutteeɓe e heeferɓe ɓe ndaganaaki heeferɓe ɓe heeferɓe ɓe kadi ndaganaaki ɓe, totteeɓe koɓe nafqi ko bakkaat alah e mon nde ndesaton ɓe si on tottii ɓe teŋe maɓɓe wote nanngite piɓle rewɓe heeferɓe naamnee ko nafquɗon kamɓe ne yo ɓe naamna ko ɓe nafqi ko, ko ɗuum woni ñaawoore Alla hakkunde mon Alla ko gannda ñeeñɗuɗo"
  60,11,Si huunde faatiima mon e rewɓe mon faade e heefereeɓe leptuɗon ɓe tottee ɓeen ɓe rewɓe mum en njahi fotde koɓe tottirno kulee Alla mbo goonɗin ɗon O
  60,12,"Eehey ma annabi si rewɓe juulɓe ngari e ma hoɓe coodandira e ma nde ɓe ndenndintah Alla e hay gooto,ngujjatah, njinatah, mbaratah sukaaɓe mum en,ngaddatah fenaande fepindaande hakkunde juuɗe mum en e koyɗe mum en,ɓe ngoopataa Ma e moƴƴere ndeen de soodandir e mum en, yaafnanoɓe Alla, pellet Alla ko jaafatooɗo jurmotooɗo"
  60,13,"Eehey mjon goonɗiɓe wote keetne yimɓe ɓe Alla tikkani e dow mum en, ɓe piɓtiima e laakara hono no heeferɓe piɓtari e yimɓe genaale"
  61,1,"Kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi seninii Allah. Ko Kanko woni Fooluɗo, Ñeeño On"
  61,2,Eehey mon goonɗinɓe ko waɗi hoɗon kaala ko on mbaɗatah
  61,3,Mawni tikkere ka Alla nde kaalaton ko on gollatah
  61,4,Pellet Alla na yiɗi ɓeen haɓateeɓe e laawol Alla hoɓe ngoni saffeeji hono maadi potndaandi
  61,5,"Tumo nde o maakani yimɓe makko, yimɓe am holko taki hoɗon lora mi te hoɗon nganndi komi nelaaɗo Alla faade e mon, ndeɓe ooñi Alla ooñi ɓerɗe maɓɓe Alla feewnatah yimɓe faasiqeeɓe"
  61,6,"E nde Iisa ɓiy Maryama maaki eehey mon banii Israa*iil komi nelaaɗo Alla tigi faade e mon goonɗinɗo ko woni ko e hakkunde juuɗe am Tawreet e beltinoowo nelaaɗo garoowo caggal hombo wiyee Ahmadu, nde o anndani ɓe hujjaaji laaɓɗi ɓe mbi*i ɗum ko mbilewu ɓanngungu"
  61,7,"Alah ɓurɗa tooñde oon pepandiiɗo e dow Alla te hombo noddee e islaam, Alla feewnatah tooñooɓe"
  61,8,"Hoɓe faala ñifrude annoore Alla nde kunduɗe maɓɓe, Alla ko timminoowo annoore makko nde haysi heefereeɓe ngañii"
  61,9,"Ko Kanko woni Nulirɗo Nulaaɗo Makko on peewal e diina goonga, fii yo o ɓamtu ka e hoore kala diina, hay si sirkooɓe ɓen añii [ɗum]"
  61,10,Eehey mon goonɗinɓe mbele mi tinndintah on njulaagu ndaɗnatngu on e lepte muusɗe
  61,11,Ngoonɗinon Alla e nelaaɗo Makko mbaɗiron jihaadi e laawol makko jawdi mon e pittaali mon ko ɗuum ɓuri on moƴƴande si on ngonii annduɓe
  61,12,"Alla hafrana on bakkatuuji mon, O naatna on aljannaaji ɗi caatli ndogata ley mum e koɗorɗe belɗe ka aljanna Adan ko ɗuum woni malal manngal. @Corrected"
  61,13,E goɗɗo mbo njiɗɗon ballal ummaade e Alla e uddital ɓadingal weltin juulɓe ɓe
  61,14,"Eehey mon goonɗinɓe ngonee wallooɓe Alla hono no Iisa Ibnu Mariya maaki suɓaaɓe mum hombo wallata mi faade e Alla suɓaaɓe mum mbii ko mjinen ngoni wallooɓe Alla, heen fedde e Banii Isra*eel goonɗini wonnde nde yeddi Min cemmbini goonɗinnde nde e dow añɓe mum en ɓe ngonti foolɓe"
  62,1,"Kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi hino seninnde Allah, Laamɗo, Seniiɗo, Fooluɗo, Ñeeño On"
  62,2,"Ko kanko nuli e humammbinneeɓe ɓen Nulaaɗo jeyaaɗo e maɓɓe, himo janngana ɓe Aayeeje Makko ɗen, o laɓɓina ɓe, o anndina ɓe Deftere nden e Sunna on, hay si tawiino ko adii ɗum, ɓe laatino e majjere ɓanngude"
  62,3,"(O nuli mo) kadi e woɗɓe goo e maɓɓe, ɓe hawrondiraali e ɓen taho. Ko Kanko woni Fooluɗo, Ñeeño On"
  62,4,"Ɗum ko ɓural Allah, Himo okka ngal mo O muuyani. Allah ko Jom ɓural mawnngal"
  62,5,"Misal ronndinaaɓe Tawreeta ɓen refti ɓe golliraali nde, no wa'i wa mbabba ronndii mba defte. Misal yimɓe fennooɓe Aayeeje Alla ɗen bonii. Allah fewnataa yimɓe tooñooɓe ɓen"
  62,6,"Maaku: \"Ko onon yo Huudiŋkooɓe ! Si on aaƴike wonnde ko on yiɗaaɓe Allah ko wanaa yimɓe heddiiɓe ɓen, haray yelee maayde, si tawii ko on goonguɓe"
  62,7,"Ɓe yelotaako nde muk, sabu ko juuɗe maɓɓe ɗen ardini kon. Allah ko annduɗo tooñooɓe ɓen"
  62,8,"Maaku: \"Ndee maayde nde dogoton, pellet, ko nde hawraynde e mon. Refti rutteɗon ka On annduɗo wirniiɗi e feeñuɗi, O humpita on ko gollaynoɗon kon"
  62,9,"Ko onon yo gomɗimɓe ! Si juulde nden noddinanaama ñalnde Juma, yaccee e jantagol Allah, acciton ngeyngu. Ko ɗum ɓuri moƴƴannde on, si tawno ko on annduɓe"
  62,10,"Si julde nden gasii, haray saakitee ka leydi, ɗaɓɓon ɓural Allah ngal [woni arsike], janntoron innde Allah ko ɗuuɗi, belajo'o on maloyte"
  62,11,"Si ɓe yi'ii ngeyngu maa fijindaaru, ɓe hammira ton, ɓe acce hiɗa darii. Maaku: \"Ko ko woni ka Allah kon ɓuri moƴƴude beleeɗe e njulaaku. Ko Allah ɓuri Moƴƴude e arsikooɓe ɓen"
  63,1,"Si naafiqiiɓe ɓen arii e maa, ɓe wi'a: \"Meɗen seedii wonnde ko a Nulaaɗo Allah\". Allah no anndi wonnde pellet, ko a Nulaaɗo Makko; Allah no seedii wonnde pellet, naafiqiiɓe ɓen ko fenooɓe"
  63,2,"Ɓe jogitorri goondooje maɓɓe ɗen heedo, ɓe sakkii laawol Allah ngol. Pellet, fii ko ɓe gollaynoo kon bonii"
  63,3,"Ɗum non ko tawde ɓe gomɗinii, refti ɓe yeddi, ɓerɗe maɓɓe ɗen notaa e mun; kamɓe on ɓe faamataa"
  63,4,"Si a yi'ii ɓe, ɓalli maɓɓe welete; si ɓe wowlii, a heɗoto konnguɗi maɓɓe ɗin. Hiɓe wa'i wa pecce ɓaaraaɗe, hiɓe sikka kala eewnaango ko e hoore maɓɓe. Ko ɓen tigi woni añɓe ɓen, reenoɓe. Allah huɗii ɓe ! Ko honno ɓe yiiltiratool (e goonga)"
  63,5,"Si ɓe wi'anaama: \"Aree Nulaaɗo Allah on insinanoo on\", ɓe hayla ko'e maɓɓe ɗen, yi'aa hiɓe ɗuurnoo hara ko ɓe townitiiɓe"
  63,6,"Hino fota e maɓɓe, foti a insinani ɓe maa hara a insinanaaki ɓe: Allah yaafotaako ɓe fes, pellet, Allah fewnataa yimɓe faasiqiiɓe ɓen"
  63,7,Ko ɓeen woni wi*ooɓe wote nafqee wonɓe e sera Nelaaɗà haa ɓe ceerta na woodani Alla moftirɗi kammuuli e leydi kono tan naafiqeeɓe ɓe paamatah
  63,8,"Hoɓe wi*a si en ruttiima Madiina ma ɓurɓe teddude yaltin ɓurɓe hoyde ɓe, woodanii Alla teddungal e nelaaɗo makko e goonɗinɓe ɓe, kono tan naafige en nganndah"
  63,9,Eehey mon goonɗinɓe woto sokli mon jawle mon e ɓiɓɓe mon gaa e innude Alla kala baɗɗo ɗuum ko ɓeen ngoni pertuɓe ɓe
  63,10,"Nafqe ko Alla arsakini on ko, ko adii nde maayde arata e gooto e mon o wiya joom am A leelnantaa kam haa e happu ɓadiiɗo mi sakkoro mi wona e moƴƴuɓe"
  63,11,Alla neemnantah hay fittaandu wooturu si happu manndu arii Alla na humpatii ko golloton ko
  64,1,"Ina subhinanoo Alla kala ko woni e kammuuli e ka leydi, na woodani Mbo laamu na woodani Mbo jettooje ko O kattanɗo kala huunde"
  64,2,Ko kanko tagi on ina e mon keefeero ina e mon goonɗinɗo Alla na yi*a ko golloton ko
  64,3,O tagrii kammuuli e leydi goongo O mbaadini on O moƴƴini mbaadiili mon ko e Makko woni battane mon
  64,4,Hombo anndi ko woni e kammuuli e leydi hombo anndi ko wirnaton e ko ɓannginton Alla na anndi ko woni e ɓerɗe
  64,5,"Mbela araani e mon kabaruuji ɓeen yedduɓe ko adi,ɓe meeɗi lepte fiyakuuji mum en woodaniiɓe lepte muusɗe"
  64,6,"Woni sabu ɗeen lepte noon ko nelaaɓe mum en na ngaddanatnoo ɓe dallillaaji ɓannguɗi ɓe wi*a ee ko ɓanndiyankooɓe peewnata min,ɓe njeddi, Alla yondanii,Alla ko galo jettaaɗo"
  64,7,"Heefereɓe ɓe aaƴiima ɓe ummintaake,maaku oho kay ma on ummine mi woondarii joom am ma on ummine,refti ma on kumpite ko golluuɗon, ɗuum na newanii Alla"
  64,8,Goonɗinee Alla e nelaaɗo makko e annoore nde O tellini pellet Alla ko kumpatiiɗo ko golloton ko
  64,9,"ñande O renndi mon ñalngu denndingol oon woni ñalngu basandiral, ka goonɗinɗo Alla o golli ko lobbi o momtone boneeji mum, O naatna mbo aljanaaji ɗi caatli ndogata les majji ɓe caasa toon haa pooma, ko ɗuum woni malal manngal. @Corrected"
  64,10,"Ko ɓeen yedduɓe penni aayeeje amen ngoni yimɓe yiite saasooɓe e henge, nge bonii battane"
  64,11,"Musiiba heɓatah hay gooto si wonah e sakkitoore Alla, kala goonɗinɗo Alla O feewna ɓernde makko, Alla na anndi kala huunde"
  64,12,"Ɗoftee Alla, ɗoftoɗon Nulaaɗo on, rentoɗon ! Si on huccitii, anndee pellet, ko fawii Nulaaɗo Amen on tun, ko yottingol ɓanngina"
  64,13,"Allaahu alah deweteeɗo e goongo si wonah Kanko, ko e dow makko goonɗinɓe mbakkilato"
  64,14,"Eehey mon goonɗinɓe pellet ina e yogo e suddiiɓe mon e ɓiɓɓe mon ko añɓe mon ndeenteeɓe, si on njaafiima on njarliima pellet Alla ko jaafatooɗo jurmotooɗo"
  64,15,"Anndee pellet, jawle mon ɗen e ɓiɗɓe mon ɓen ko fitina ina ka Alla njoɓdi mawndi"
  64,16,"Kulee Alla ko kattanɗon nanee ɗoftaɗon nafqe ko ɗuum ɓuri moƴƴande pittaali mon, oon deenaaɗo fittaandu makko e ɗawre, ko ɓeen ngoni malaaɓe ɓe"
  64,17,"Si on ñamlii Alla ñamaande moƴƴere O sowana ɗum en nde, O yaafoɓe Alla ko jettoowo ko muñɗo"
  64,18,"Annduɗo wirniiɗi e feeñuɗi, Mawɗo, ñeeñɗuɗo"
  65,1,"Eehey ma annabi si on ceerii suddiiɓe ceereeɓe e edda mum en tonnge edda o, kulee Alla joomi mon wotee njaltineeɓe e cuuɗi mum en wotoɓe njaltu si wonah ɓe mbaɗ pankare peeñɗe ko ɗiin ngoni keeri Alla kala jawtuɗo keerol Alla o tooñi hoore makko, a anndah yaama de Alla waɗata caggal ɗuum fiyaaku"
  65,2,"Si ɓe yottinii edda mum en nanngireeɓe no moƴƴi wollo ceerdonɓe no moƴƴi,ceednon seedeeji ɗiɗi ummaade e mon ndarnee seedanfaagal fii Alla ko ɗuum woni ko waajete wonande oon goonɗinɗo Alla e ñalnde sakkatiinde kala deentiiɗo Alla,Alla waɗana mbo yaltirde"
  65,3,"O arsikina mbo to o sikkaana, kala bakkaliiɗo e Alla yonii mbo, pellet yamiroore Alla nde ko yottotoonde, Alla waɗanii kala huunde fotde mum"
  65,4,"ɓeen suddiiɓe mon fiɓtiiɓe fiilayru si on cikkatiima edda mum en ko lebbi tati e ɓeen ɓe piilataako edda mum en ko lebbi tati, debadeedi en noon edda maɓɓe gasata ko nde ɓe njibini, kala kulɗo Alla O waɗana mbo newaare e fiyaaku makko"
  65,5,"ɗuum ko ñaawoore Alla O tellaniinde e mon, kala kulɗo Alla O hafrana mbo bakkatuuji makko, O mawninana mbo njoɓdi"
  65,6,"Koɗneeɓe ɗo koɗɗon fotde kattane mon wotee loreeɓe ngam ɓittinandeɓe, nafqeeɓe haa ɓe keɓto tawde koɓe korinoo ɓe, si wonii ɓe muyninanii on njonnee ɓe njoɓdi mum en njandire moƴƴere hakkunde mon, si on cattiraama yo goɗɗo muynin mbo"
  65,7,"Yo nafqu gala e ngalu makko he, oon paaɗaaɗo noon yo nafqu e ko Alla totti mbo ko,Alla fawatah hay fittaandu si wonah ko tottindu ko, ma Alla waɗ caggal satteende newuya"
  65,8,"Heewii saare saliinde yamiroore joom mum e nelaaɓo mum, min kaasbii nde haasbo sattungo Min leptinnde lepte bonɗe"
  65,9,Nde meeɗi lepte golle mayre laati batte fiyaaku mayre ko perte
  65,10,"Alla heblaniɓe lepte cattuɗe kulee Alla onon joman en hakkillaaji ɓeen goonɗinɓe, Alla tellinii e mum en ko siftinta"
  65,11,"Nelaaɗo taratooɗo e mon aayeeje ɓannguɗe ngam O yaltina ɓeen goonɗin ɓe golluɓe golle lobbe ummaade e niwre faade e annoore, kala goonɗinɗo Alla golli ko moƴƴi O naatna mbo aljannaaji ɗi caatli ilata les majji ɓe nduumo toon, ko goongo Alla moƴƴinanii mbo arsuka. @Corrected"
  65,12,"Alla tagɗo kammuuli jeeɗiɗi e leydi yeru majji, yamiroore Alla na tello hakkunde majji ngam nganndon wonde Alla ko kattanɗo kala huunde Alla fiiltariima kala huunde e ganndal"
  66,1,"Eehey ma annabi ko taki ana harmina ko Alla dagnan ma sabu ɗaɓɓude welnaade suddiiɓe ma, Alla ko jaafatooɗo jurmotooɗo"
  66,2,Alla farlii e mon dagtinde goondooje mon Alla ko keedo mon ko kanko woni ganndo Ñeeñƴudo
  66,3,"Tuma nde annabi deeyi faade e yogo e suddiiɓe makko yeewtere, nde o habri yeewtere nde, Alla feññinani mbo O anndini yogo e yeewtere he, O falii heen yogo, nde O habri mbo ɗum o wi*i hombo habru ma ɗum O maaki habrii kam Gannda Kumpatiiɗo"
  66,4,"Si on tuubi faade e Alla sabu ɓerɗe mon ɗe ooñinooma si on wallandirii e dow makko, ko Alla woni ballo makko e jIbriil e goonɗinɓe moƴƴuɓe e Malayka en caggal ɗum koɗi ballooji"
  66,5,Yaama de joom makko si O ceeriiɓe nde O wostantoo mbo ɓurɓe mon moƴƴude juulɓe goonɗinɓe ɗoftiiɓe tuubooɓe rewooɓe Alla hoorooɓe Seemedɓe e boomi
  66,6,Eehey mon goonɗinɓe ndeene ko*e mon e koreeji mon e yiite docate mannge ko yimɓe e kaaƴe ina e dow henge malaykaaji tekkuɗi cattuɗi ɗi ngoopatah ko Alla yamariɗi te hoɗi ngolla ko Alla yamiriɗi
  66,7,Eehey mon heeferɓe wote ngantinee hannde njoɓeteɗon tan koko ngollatna ɗon
  66,8,"Eehey mon goonɗinɓe tuubee faade e Alla tuubgol laaɓngol yaama joomi mon hafrana on bonɗi mon O naatna mon aljannaaji na ila ley majji caatli, ñande Alla hoynatah annabi e ɓeen goonɗinɓe wondude e mum, annoore mum en na yaha yeesa mum en e ñaama mum en hoɓe mbiya joomi amen timminan amen annoore amen yaafa min pellet ko a kattanɗo kala huunde. @Corrected"
  66,9,"Ko an yo Annabiijo, haɓ e heeferɓe ɓen e naafiqiiɓe ɓen, saɗtinanaa ɓe; weerde maɓɓe nden ko Jahannama, nge bonii ruttorde"
  66,10,"Alla fiyani misal wonande ɓeen yedduɓe soknaaja Nuuhu e luutu ɓe ngoniina e les jiyaaɓe amen ɗiɗo moƴƴuɓe ɓe njanfiiɓe ɗuum nafaaniɓe ka Alla hay huunde,ɓe wi*e naatee yiite wondude e naatɓe ɓe"
  66,11,"Alla fiyani misal goonɗinɓe ɓe debbo fir*awna nde o wiino joom am mahanam ka Ma suudu ka aljanna ndaɗndaa mi e fir*awna e golle mum, daɗndam e yimɓe tooñooɓe"
  66,12,E Maryama ɓiy imraana oon reeni hoore makko e jina Min ngutti heen ruuhu amen o goonɗini konngi joomiiko e defte Makko o tawa e ɗoftiiɓe ɓe
  67,1,"Mo laamu woni e juuɗe Mun On mawnii, ko Kanko woni hattanɗo kala huunde"
  67,2,"On tagirɗo maayde e nguurndam, fii ndaarndagol on ko hommbo e mo'on ɓuri moƴƴude golle. Ko Kanko woni Fooluɗo, Haforoowo On"
  67,3,On taguɗo kammuuli jeeɗiɗi fawondirɗi. A yi'ataa ɓura-ɓurda e tagu Jom hinaraŋke On. Yiltu ndaarɗe maa ɗen (daaraa). Taw si a yi'ay ceekol
  67,4,"Refti ruttaa ndaarɗe ɗen laaɓi ɗiɗi, gite maa ɗen ruttoto e maaɗa hara ko ɗe hoyɗe, taƴiiɗe"
  67,5,"Gomɗii Men cuɗinirii kammu aduna ngun [koode] pitilli, Men waɗi ɗe fiɗirɗe seytanuuji, Men hebilani ɓe lette Huɓɓunge negn"
  67,6,"Hino woodani ɓen yedduɓe Joomi mun, lette Jahannama. Nge bonii ruttorde"
  67,7,"Si ɓe weddaama e nder magge, ɓe naniray nge haacaango, hara hinge fata"
  67,8,"Hinge eɓɓa fultagol, sabu tikkere nden. Tuma kala nde dental bugaa e magge, ayninaaɓe nge ɓen lamndoo ɓe : \"E hara jertinoowo araano e mo'on"
  67,9,"Ɓe wi'a: \"Pellet ! Jertinoowo aruno e amen tigi, kono men fenni men wi'i: Allah jippinaali hay e huunde, on wonaali si wanaa e nder majjere mawnde"
  67,10,"Ɓe wi'ita : \"Si meɗen nanaynoo maa hara meɗen haqqilaynoo, men jeyetanooke e yimɓe Huɓɓunge ngen"
  67,11,Ɓe qirritii junuubi maɓɓe ɗin. Halakuyee woodanii jom en Huɓɓaynge ngen
  67,12,"Pellet, hulooɓe Joomi mun ɓen ka wirnii, hino woodani ɓen haforaneede e njoɓdi mawndi"
  67,13,Suuɗee konnguɗi mon maa ɓanninon ɗum. Kanko On ko O annduɗo ko woni e nder ɓerɗe
  67,14,"E hara taguɗo On anndaa? Ko Kanko le woni Newiiɗo, Humpitiiɗo On"
  67,15,"Ko Kanko waɗani on leydi ndin eltaandi : haray yehee e seraaji mayri, ñaamon e arsike Makko. Ko ka Makko woni ummital ngal"
  67,16,"E on hooli On wonɗo ka kammu nde O munnataa e mo'on leydi ndin, Tawa yoo hindi dilla? @Corrected"
  67,17,Kaa on hooli On wonɗo ka kammu nde O wurtataa e mon henndu bippooru? Aray nde anndon ko honno woni jertinaango Am ngon
  67,18,Sellii adinooɓe ɓen ɗon ɓen fenniino. Taskii ko honno lette Am ɗen wattinirnoo
  67,19,"E ɓee yi'aali colli ɗin dow maɓɓe, hiɗi fonta gabitannji ɗi ñobba? [Wonnde] jogitaaki ɗin si wanaa Jom hinaraŋke On. Pellet, ko O reenuɗo kala huunde"
  67,20,"E ko hommbo woni on konuujo mum wallata on hara wanaa Jom hinaraŋke On? Tigi on, heeferɓe ɓen wonaali si wanaa e nder hodo"
  67,21,"E ko hommbo woni arsikoowo on, si O jogitike arsike Makko on? Si ko woni, ɓe duumike e ƴaggere e woɗɗitagol"
  67,22,Kere ko on yahoowo no hippi yeeso mun ɓuri feewude? Kaa ko on yahoowo no fotondiri e laawol focciingol
  67,23,"Maaku: \"Ko Kanko woni ko fuɗɗi on, O waɗani on nanɗe e giiɗe e ɓerɗe\". Kono fanɗii ko yettoton [neema]"
  67,24,"Maaku: \"Ko Kanko woni saakituɗo on leydi, ko ka Makko kadi woni ko mooɓitoyteɗon"
  67,25,"Hiɓe wi'a: \"Ko honnde tuma woni ndee fodoore, si tawii ko on goonguɓe"
  67,26,"Maaku : \"Anndee anndugol [fii Darnagl] ko ka Allah woni. Min on ko Mi jertinoowo [tun] ɓanngina"
  67,27,"Nde ɓe yi'oyta (lette) ɗen ka ɓadii, geece yedduɓe ɓen suni geece heeferɓe, [ɓe] wi'anee : \"Ko ɗum ɗoo woni ko ɗaɓɓaynoɗon"
  67,28,"Maaku : \"Yeetee lam, si Allah ƴettitii lam min e wonndiiɓe am maa O yurmaama men, ko hommbo daɗndata heeferɓe ɓen lette muusuɗe"
  67,29,"Maaku : \"Ko Kanko Jom hinaraŋke On. Men gomɗinii Mo, ko e Makko kadi men fawii. Aray nde anndon ko hommbo woni e majjere ɓanngunde"
  67,30,"Maaku : \"Yeetee lam, si ndiyam mon ɗam wattinii ɓeeɓuɗam, ko hommbo addanta on ndiyam ilayɗam"
  68,1,Nuun. Mi woondirii karambol e ko ɓe winndirta kon
  68,2,"Aan a wonaa, sabu neema Joomi maa on, haangaaɗo"
  68,3,"Ko pellet, hino woodan-maa njoɓdi ndi taƴondirtaa"
  68,4,"E ko pellet, hiɗa e jikku mawngu"
  68,5,"Aray nde tinaa, ɓe yi'a kamɓe kadi"
  68,6,ko hommbo e mo'on woni haangaaɗo on
  68,7,"Pellet, ko Joomi maa ɓuri anndude majjuɗo on laawol Makko ngol, ko Kanko kadi ɓuri anndude feewuɓe ɓen"
  68,8,Wata a tewto fennooɓe ɓen
  68,9,"Hiɓe yiɗi si a newantono (ɓe), ɓe newano-(maa)"
  68,10,"Wata a tewto kadi kala ɗuuɗuɗo woondugol, hoyɗo"
  68,11,"ɗuuɗuɗo nyo*ugol, ɗuuɗuɗo yaarugol baddi"
  68,12,"ɗuuɗuɗo haɗugol moƴƴere, jaggitoowo, bakkondinɗo"
  68,13,"yoora-ɓerndeejo e hoore ɗum, heɓiraaɗo nii"
  68,14,fii o wonii jom jawdi e ɓiɗɓe
  68,15,"Si Aayeeje Amen ɗen janngaama e [tawnde] makko, o wi'a: \"Ko tinndi adinooɓe"
  68,16,Aray nde Men maandina mo e hoore kinal
  68,17,"Men jarribor ɓe wano Men jarribornoo jeyɓe ngesa mba : fewndo ɓen woondunoo pellet, ɓe soñay mba subaka ko ɓe dawuɓe"
  68,18,"ɓe ittintinaali [wiide] :\"Si Allah jaɓii"
  68,19,Yiite immori ka Joomi maa ari huuɓiti mba tawi hiɓe ɗaanii
  68,20,mba wa'iti wa jemma ɓaleejo
  68,21,Ɓe noddindiri bimmbi on
  68,22,"Kori dawee ka ngesa mon, si tawii ko on soñooɓe"
  68,23,Ɓe hucciti hiɓe ɓɗuumbo
  68,24,"Wonnde \"Miskiino woo naatataa e mabba hannde"
  68,25,"Ɓe ndawidi e ɗawugol [waasuɓe ɓen] ko ɓe eɓɓuɓe"
  68,26,"Nde ɓe yi'unoo mba, ɓe wi'i: \"Pellet, men majjii [laawol ngol]"
  68,27,wurin ko men ɗawaaɓe
  68,28,"Ɓurɗo ɓe moƴƴude on wi'i: \"Mi wi'anaano on : haanii ko subbunhinoɗon"
  68,29,"Ɓe wi'i: \"Senaade woodanii Joomi amen ! Pellet, hari ko men tooñuɓe"
  68,30,"Woɗɓe e maɓɓe fewtiti ɓeya, hiɓe felindira"
  68,31,"Ɓe wi'i: \"Ee bone amen ! Pellet, hari ko men bewuɓe"
  68,32,"Hino gasa ka Joomi amen wattitana men ɓuri mban ɗon moƴƴude. Ko ka Joomi amen ko min reerɗube e [yaafeede]"
  68,33,"Ko non tigi woni lette ɗen; ko lette laakara ɗen non ɓuri manude, sinno hiɓe anndunoo"
  68,34,"Pellet, hino woodani gomɗuɓe ɓen ka Joomi maɓɓe, Aljannaaji neema"
  68,35,Kere Men waɗay jebbiliiɓe ɓen wano bomɓe ɓen
  68,36,"Ko heɓi on, si ɗon ñaawira non"
  68,37,"Kaa hiɗon mari Deftere, nde janngoton e mun"
  68,38,"Pellet, ko woodani on e mayre, ko ko suɓotoɗon"
  68,39,"Kaa ko fodooje woodani on e Amen, hoolniiɗe haa Ñalnde Darngal, wonnde pellet, hino woodani on ko ñaawoton kon"
  68,40,Lamndii ɓe ko hommbo e maɓɓe fawtaniiɓe ɗum
  68,41,"Kaa ko kafidiiɓe woodani ɓe? Awa yo ɓe addu kafidiiɓe maɓɓe ɓen, si tawii ko ɓe goonguɓe"
  68,42,"Ñalnde belenru ñoroytee, ɓe noddee e sujjugol kono hara ɓe waawataa. @Corrected"
  68,43,"Hara gite maɓɓe ɗen no heli, koyeera no suddi ɓe. Ko tawde ɓe noddeteno e sujjugol fewndo ka ɓe waawunoo"
  68,44,Accidam e kala fennuɗo ndee yewtere; aray nde Men suynira ɓe nokku ka ɓe anndaa
  68,45,"Miɗo nennan ɓe. Pellet non, pewje Am ɗen ko tiiɗuɗe"
  68,46,"Kaa a lamndi ɓe njoɓdi, hara ko yoɓugol ndi teddani ɓe"
  68,47,"Kaa ɓe anndu fii wirniiɗi ɗin, hara hiɓe winndira [ɗim hujjaaji maɓɓe]"
  68,48,"Muññor ñaawoore Joomi maa nden, hara a wa'aali wa wonndiiɗo linngii ngii fewndo o noddunoo [Joomi makko] himo sunii"
  68,49,"Si tawno moƴƴere immorde e Joomi makko hewtitanooki mo, ko pellet, o bugeteno e wulaa hara ko o felniiɗo"
  68,50,"Joomi makko suɓii mo, O waɗi mo e moƴƴuɓe ɓen"
  68,51,"Hay yedduɓe ɓen eɓɓiinoo yuwirgol ma gite maɓɓe ɗen, nde ɓe nanunoo Janntoore nden, hiɓe wi'a: \"On ko haangaaɗo"
  68,52,"Ndee [Alqur’aanaare] wonaali, si wanaa waaju tageefo ngon"
  69,1,Darngal
  69,2,Ko honɗum woni Darngal
  69,3,Ko honɗum anndin maa ko woni Darngal
  69,4,Samuudu e Aadi en fennii duɗɗugol Darngal
  69,5,"Si ko Samuuda en, ɓe halkira haacaango"
  69,6,"Aadi en kan, ɓe halkira henndu bippooru hattinndu tiiɗude"
  69,7,"O elti ndu e hoore maɓɓe jemmaaji jeeɗiɗi e ñalormaaje jeetati jokkondirɗe; yi'aa yimɓe ɓen no pukkii e ɗin [koɗooli] wa si tawii ko ɓe daƴƴe tamaro irtiiɗe"
  69,8,Taw si a yi'anay ɓe ko heddii
  69,9,Fir'awna e adinooɓe mo e ca'e junnitanooɗe ɗen ardi e goopi
  69,10,"ɓe yeddi Nulaaɗo Joomi maɓɓe on, O nanngiri ɓe nanngal sattungal"
  69,11,"Ko Menen woni, fewndo ndiyam ɗam hummbunoo, Min roondi on ka dogayka"
  69,12,"fii no Men waɗirana ɗum waaju, nowru nanayndu nana ɗum"
  69,13,Si wuttaama ka allaandu wuttaande wootere
  69,14,leydi ndin e pelle ɗen ɓamtee moññe mo ɓññannde wootere
  69,15,"Nden ñalnde, Darngal ngal daroto"
  69,16,"Kammu ngun seekoo, hara ko ngu lo'ungu nden ñalnde"
  69,17,"Hara Malaa'ika'en wontira ka seraaji maggu, njeetato [e maɓɓe] ronndoo Arsi Joomi maa kin e hoore maɓɓe nden ñalnde"
  69,18,Nden ñalnde ko on weeɓitetee; hay huunde e fii mon suuɗotaako
  69,19,"Si ko jonnitiroyaaɗo talkuru mun ndun ka ñaamo mun, o wi'oyay : \"Jaɓee ! Janngon talkuru am ndun"
  69,20,Min mi fellituno mi hawroygol e hasboore am moƴƴere nden
  69,21,Hara himo e nguurndam welɗam
  69,22,E nder Aljanna toowuɗo
  69,23,mo dimɗe mun ɓadii
  69,24,"Ñaamee yariron no newori, sabu ko ardin-ɗon kon e ñalaaɗe feƴƴuɗe"
  69,25,"Si tawii non ko jonntiiroyaaɗo talkuru mun ndun ka nano mun, on wi'oyay : \"Haaaniino lam hara mi jonnitaaka talkuru am ndun"
  69,26,Hara mi anndaali ko woni ñaawoore am
  69,27,"Hara [maayde] nden wononu timmoode [am]"
  69,28,Jawdi am ndin duncanaali lam
  69,29,Mbaawko am kon halkirii lam
  69,30,Nanngee mo kolmbon bmo
  69,31,refti naadon mo ka Jahiimi
  69,32,refti naadon mo e jolokooje-callale- ɗe juuteendi mun woni cogone cappanɗe jeeɗiɗi
  69,33,Tawde o gomɗinaano Allah Mawɗo On
  69,34,O reerɗintaa e ñammiingol miskiino
  69,35,Giɗo ɓadondiraaɗo alanaamo ɗoo hannde
  69,36,"wanaa ñaametee, si wanaa e ƴiƴƴiƴiri"
  69,37,"Ñaamataa ndin, si wanaa bakkondimɓe ɓen"
  69,38,Mi woondirii ko yi'oton kon
  69,39,E ko on yi'ataa kon
  69,40,"wonnde pellet, [Alqur'aana] ko konngol Nulaaɗo tedduɗo"
  69,41,wanaa nde konnguɗi yimoowo; kono fanɗii ko gomɗinton
  69,42,"wanaa kadi nde konnguɗi mbileejo, kono famɗii ko waajitotoɗon"
  69,43,ko jippiniraande ka Jeyɗo Winndere nden
  69,44,Si tawno o fefindino e Amen yoga e konnguɗi
  69,45,"ko pellet, Men nanngirayno mo doole"
  69,46,Hooti Men taƴayno e makko ɗaɗol ɓernde ngol
  69,47,Alaa e mo'on hay gooto haɗoowo Men e makko
  69,48,"Pellet, ndee [Alqur'aanaare] konde waajitorgol gomɗuɓe ɓen"
  69,49,"Haray kadi, Meɗen anndi ina e mon fennooɓe [nde]"
  69,50,"ko pellet non, ɗum ko nimse e hoore yedduɓe ɓen"
  69,51,"pellet kadi, ko nde goonga yananaaɗo"
  69,52,"Haray subbunhinor innde Joomi maa, Mawɗo On"
  70,1,Torotooɗo torike lette yanayɗe
  70,2,"wonannde heeferɓe ɓen, alaa duñanoowo ɓe ɗe"
  70,3,"ko immorde ka Allah, Jom ƴawruɗe"
  70,4,"Malaa'ka'en wonndude e Jibriilu hino ƴawa faade e Makko, e nder ñalaande nde eɓɓoore mun woni duuɓi ujune cappanɗe jowi"
  70,5,"Muñño tun, muñal labaangal"
  70,6,Kamɓe hiɓe yi*a (lette) ɗen ko woɗɗuɗe
  70,7,Meɗen reeni ɗe Menen ko ɓadiiɗe
  70,8,Ñalnde kammu ngun wa'oyta wa ko taayinaa
  70,9,pelle ɗen wa'oya wa hottolle kardaako
  70,10,ka ɓadondiraaɗo lamdotaako fii jeydaaɗo mun
  70,11,"Hiɓe hollindiree. Bonɗo on yeloto sottorgol lette ɗen nden ñalnde, ɓiɗɓe makko ɓen"
  70,12,"e gennda makko, e neene gooto makko on"
  70,13,e gorol makko ngol moolayngol mo
  70,14,"e kala wonɓe ka leydi ɓen, fii no ɗum daɗndira mo"
  70,15,"Ɗum gasataa. Ngen [Yiite] ko uuyunge"
  70,16,ɓoltaynge guri hoore
  70,17,Hinge nodda on ɗuurniiɗo o hucciti
  70,18,o mooɓi (jawle) o mari e marirgel
  70,19,"Pellet, neɗɗo tagaama ko o ɗenƴotooɗo"
  70,20,"si bone memii mo, o faaya"
  70,21,"si ko mo moƴƴere heɓi mo, o salora"
  70,22,Si wanaa juulooɓe ɓen. @Corrected
  70,23,ɓen tawɓe ko ɓe duumiiɓe e juulde maɓɓe nden
  70,24,E ɓen tawɓe hino ka jawle maɓɓe haqqee anndaaɗo
  70,25,wonannde torotooɗo e haɗitiiɗi
  70,26,e ɓen gomɗimɓe ñalaande njoɓdi diina
  70,27,E ɓen tawɓe ko ɓe huluɓe lette Joomi maɓɓe ɗen
  70,28,"tawde pellet, lette Joomi maɓɓe ɗen wanaa hoolniiɗe"
  70,29,E ɓen tawɓe ko reenuɓe farjuuji maɓɓe ɗin
  70,30,"si wanaa e rewɓe maɓɓe maa ɓen horɓe maɓɓe ɓe ɓe jeyiri ñaame maɓɓe, ɗon on ɓe feletaake"
  70,31,"Kala non ɗaɓɓuɗo [ka dakmitora] caggal ɗum, haray ko ɓen woni jaggituɓe ɓen"
  70,32,E ɓen tawɓe ko aynituɓe koolaaje e aadiiji maɓɓe ɗin
  70,33,E ɓen tawɓe ko ñiiɓuɓe e seedeeji mun
  70,34,e ɓen tawɓe ko reenooɓe e juulde maɓɓe nden
  70,35,Ɓen ɗon ko teddinoyteeɓe e Aljannaaji
  70,36,"E ko heɓi yedduɓe ɓen takko maaɗa, hiɓe heñora"
  70,37,"ka nano e ka ñaamo, ko ɓe dentoy-dentoy"
  70,38,Hara gooto kala e maɓɓe tamƴinoto naatoygol Aljanna neemaaji
  70,39,Ɗun waɗataa ! Men tagiriɓe ko ɓe anndi
  70,40,"Mi woondirii Jeyɗo fuɗirɗe e mutirɗe On, pellet, ko Men hattanɓe"
  70,41,"wattitirgol ɓe ko ɓuri ɓe moƴƴude, Men siforaa ronkugol [ɗum]"
  70,42,"Accuɓe ɓe jumpa, ɓe fija haa ɓe hawroya e ñalaande maɓɓe nde ɓe kammbirananoo"
  70,43,"ñalnde ɓe yaltiroyta e genaale ɗen heñaare, wa si tawii ko kaaƴe (sanamu) ɓe woni wugganaade"
  70,44,"Hara gite maɓɓe no heli, koyeera no suddi ɓe. Ko nden ñalaande woni ko ɓe kammbirananoo"
  71,1,"Men nulii Nuuhu haa e yimɓe makko ɓen, wonnde : \"Jertin yimɓe maa ɓen, ado lette muusuɗe arde e maɓɓe"
  71,2,"O maakani [ɓe] : \"Ko onon yo yimɓe am, min ko mi jertinoowo on ɓannguɗo"
  71,3,"wonnde yo on rewu Allah, hulon Mo, ɗoftoɗon lam"
  71,4,"O haforanay on junuubi mon ɗin, O nenna on haa e lajal taƴaangal. [Ko woni tun] lajal Allah ngal si hewtii, ngal nennetaake, si tawii hiɗon anndunoo"
  71,5,"O maaki : \"Joomi am, min mi noddirii yimɓe am ɓen jemma e ñalorma"
  71,6,"kono noddaandu am ndun ɓeydaali ɓe, si wanaa dogugol"
  71,7,"Tuma kala kadi nde mi noddi ɓe fii no Hafaranaa ɓe, ɓe waɗay kolli maɓɓe ɗin ka nder noppi maɓɓe, ɓe buumora comci maɓɓe ɗin, ɓe deppitoo, ɓe townitora townitaadee"
  71,8,Refti mi noddirii ɓe e kene
  71,9,"Refti mi feññinani ɓe, mi gunndii ɓe gunndaadee"
  71,10,"Mi wi'i [ɓe] : \"Insinanee Joomi mon, tawde O siforii wonnde Haforoow"
  71,11,O wurtira toɓo ngon e mo'on rewnindiral
  71,12,"O ɓeydira on jawle e ɓiɗɓe, O waɗana on gese, O waɗana on canɗi"
  71,13,"E ko heɓi on, on jortaaki manngural Allah ngal"
  71,14,Hara le O tagir on taaɓe-taaɓe
  71,15,E on yi'aali no Allah tagiri kammuulli jeeɗiɗi tegondirɗi
  71,16,"O waɗi lewru ndun jalɓundu e majji, O waɗi naange ngen pitilol"
  71,17,Ko Allah fuɗniri on ka leydi fuɗnugol
  71,18,"refti O ruttiray on e mayri, O yaltina on yaltinndee"
  71,19,Allah waɗiranii on leydi ndin weertaandi
  71,20,fii yo on naatir e mayri laawi yaajuɗi
  71,21,"Nuuhu maaki : \"Joomi am, ɓee yeddii lam, ɓe jokkii on mo jawle mun e ɓiɗɓe ɓeydaali ɗum si wanaa hayrugol"
  71,22,Ɓe fewji feere mawnde
  71,23,"ɓe wi'i: \"Wata on terto dey reweteeɗi mon ɗin: wata on terto Wudda, e Suwaa'a, e Ya'uuqatha, e Nasr"
  71,24,"Ko pellet, ɓe majjinii ko ɗuuɗi. [Joomi] wata A ɓeydir tooñuɓe ɓen, si wanaa majjere"
  71,25,"Ko sagu goopi maɓɓe ɗin ɓe yooliranoo, ɓe naadaa Yiite, ɓe heɓanaano ko'e maɓɓe faabotooɗo gaanin Allah"
  71,26,"Nuuhu maaki kadi : \"Joomi am, wata A accu e leydi ndin, hay keefeero dilloowo"
  71,27,"Ko pellet, si A accii ɓe, ɓe majjinay jeyaaɓe Maa ɓen, ɓe jiidoytaako si wanaa bonnooɓe ɗuuɗuɓe geddi"
  71,28,"Joomi am, haforanam min e jibimɓe lam ɓen, e ɓen gomɗimɓe naatuɓe ka suudu am, e gomɗimɓe worɓe ɓen e gomɗimɓe rewɓe ɓen; wata A ɓeydir tooñuɓe ɓen, si wanaa halakuyee"
  72,1,"Maaku : \"Wahayinaama e am, wonnde dental jinna heɗino [lam miɗo jannga Alqur'aana], ɗi wi'i: \"Menen men nani janngeteende haawniinde"
  72,2,"Hinde ɗowira e peewal. Men gomɗinii nde. Men kafidatah e Joomi amen, hay e gooto"
  72,3,"E wonnde manngural Joomi amen ngal mawnii, O siforaali jogitagol genndo, wanaa ɓiɗɗo"
  72,4,"E wonnde [Ibuliisa] ɗayɗo on e amen hino wowlaynoo penaale e hoore Allah"
  72,5,Menen men sikkuno wonnde yimɓe e jinna wowlataano fenaande e hoore Allah
  72,6,"Hari le worɓe yimɓe hino mooloraynoo worɓe jinna, ɓe ɓeydi ɗi bewre"
  72,7,"Kamɓe [yimɓe ɓen] ɓe sikkir no sikkirɗon non, wonnde Allah immintintah hay gooto"
  72,8,"E wonnde men meemii kammu ngun, men tawi hingu hebbiniraa aynooɓe tiiɗuɓe e docote"
  72,9,"E wonnde meɗen jooɗotonoo ton fii heɗagol. Kala non heɗitiiɗo jooni, o hawray e docotal tommbingal"
  72,10,"E wonnde men anndaa si ko bone faandanaa wonɓe ka leydi ɓen, kaa hara Joomi maɓɓe faandani ɓe peewal"
  72,11,"E wonnde hino e amen moƴƴuɗi, hino e amen kadi ko jaasi ɗum. Hari meɗen e laawi seertuɗi"
  72,12,"E wonnde men fellituno men laawotaako Allah ka hoore leydi, e wonnde men laawortaa Mo dogugol"
  72,13,"E wonnde nde men nanunoo peewal nagl, men gomɗini ngal. Kala gomɗinɗo Joomi mun, on hulataa ɗuytaneede [moƴƴi] wanaa ɓeydaneede [bonɗi]"
  72,14,"E wonnde hino e amen jebbiliiɗi, hino e amen kadi ooñiiɗi. Kala jebbilii ngii, ɗin ɗon faandike peewal"
  72,15,"Ooñiiɗi ɗin kan, ɗi laatanike Jahannama on carmalle"
  72,16,"E wonnde si ɓe ñiiɓuno e hoore laawol ngol, ko pellet, Men yarnayno ɓe ndiyam ɗuuɗuɗam"
  72,17,"fii yo Men ndaarndoro ɓe heen. Kala ɗuurniiɗo e jantoore Joomi mun nden, O naaday mo e lette sattuɗe"
  72,18,E wonnde juulirɗe ɗen ko Allah heeranii. Wata on kafidu e Allah hay e gooto
  72,19,"E wonnde tuma jeyaaɗo Allah on darinoo himo rewa Mo, ɗi ɗeɓuno waɗɗondirgol e hoore makko"
  72,20,"Maaku : \"Anndee ko Joomi am (tun) mi rewata, mi kafidataa Mo kadi hay e gooto"
  72,21,"Maaku : \"Min on mi waawanaa on duñude lorra, wanaa fii pooɗugol nafa"
  72,22,"Maaku : \"Hay gooto waawaa daɗndugol lam e Allah; mi heɓataa ko woori Mo ƴooñorde"
  72,23,"si wanaa yottingol immorde e Allah e nule Makko ɗen. Kala yedduɗo Allah e Nulaaɗo Makko on, haray ko Yiite Jahannama woodani mo, ɓe luttay e magge poomaa"
  72,24,"Haa si ɓe yi'ii ko ɓe kammbirananoo kon, ɓe aray anndude ko hombo ɓuri lo'ude ballo, ɓuri kadi fanɗude limoore"
  72,25,"Maaku : \"Mi anndaa si ko kammbiranaɗon kon hino ɓadii, maa si Joomi am waɗanay ɗum dumunna"
  72,26,Ko O ganndo wirniiɗi. O ƴellintinantaa wirniiɗi Makko ɗin hay e gooto
  72,27,"si wanaa mo O welanaa e Nulaaɗo, O naadnay yeeso on e ɓaawo makko tommbotooɓe"
  72,28,"fii yo o anndu wonnde ɓen yottinii nule Joomi maɓɓe ɗen. O huɓindorii (anndugol) ko woni ka maɓɓe kon, O mofti limoore kala huunde"
  73,1,"Ko an yo buumorɗo [comci mun]"
  73,2,"Ɓaŋo (wuurnitaa) jemma on, si wanaa seeɗa [e makko]"
  73,3,"feccere makko, maa ɗuytaa seeɗa e ɗum"
  73,4,maa ɓeydaa ɗon. Janngiraa Alqur'aanaare nden rewnindiral
  73,5,Meɗen saatii tellinnde e maaɗa konngol teddungol
  73,6,"Pellet, ko dewal tummbo jemma ngal, ɓuri tiiɗude batte e fooccaade konngol"
  73,7,"Anndu hino woodan-maa e ñalorma on, ferlitagol juutungol"
  73,8,"Janto innde Joomi maa nden, taƴo-ɗaa yahaa e Makko hattirde taƴagol"
  73,9,"Jeyɗo On fuɗnaange e hiirnaange.Reweteeɗo woo alaa e si nwona Kanko,Jogito Mo hoolorteeɗo"
  73,10,Muñño e ko ɓe wowlata kon; woɗɗito-raa ɓe woɗɗitannde labaande
  73,11,Accidam e fennooɓe joomiraaɓe neemaaji ɓen; habbito-ɗaa ɓe seeɗa
  73,12,"Ko pellet, hino ka Amen gaa : Tonngii e Jahiimi"
  73,13,"e ñaametee ɗeɗɗoowo, e lette muusuɗe"
  73,14,"Ñalnde leydi ndin e pelle ɗen dillata, pelle ɗen wa'a wa njaare ilayndi"
  73,15,Min nelii e mon nelaaɗo haa o wona seede e dow mon hono no Min nelduno faade e Fir*awna Nelaaɗo
  73,16,Fir*awna woopi nelaaɗo O Min nanngi mbo nanngugol cattungol
  73,17,Hono ndeenraton pittaali mon si on yeddi ñalawmo baɗoowo sukaaɓe danndalinde
  73,18,Kammu o na fetti e kulhuli hembo laatiima fodoore Alla ko wonoore
  73,19,Ko oon woni waaju goongo kala faalaaɗo daɗde nanngira joomiiko ruttorde
  73,20,"Pellet joom Ma na anndi haɗa juula ko ɓuri famɗude e tataɓal jemma wollo feccere mammbo wondude e fedde e ɓeen wonduɓe e Ma Alla hoddira jemma e ñalawma O anndi on tonngataa mbo O yaafii mon, njannge ko newanii on e Quraana hombo anndi ma won e mon ñawɓe goo ngona e ɗatngal ka leydi hoɓe ndaarta ɓural Alla woɓɓe kadi na kaɓano laawol Alla njannge ko newanii mon e hembo ndarnon juulde tottiron askal ñamlon Alla ñamaande moƴƴere kala ko mbaɗaɗon ko*e mon e jam tawon mbo ka Alla hombo ɓuri moƴƴude e mawnude njobdi njaafnee Alla sabu Alla ko jaafatooɗo ko jurmotooɗo"
  74,1,Ko an yo mojiiɗo
  74,2,Ɓaŋo waajo-ɗaa
  74,3,"Fii Joomi maa, mawninaa"
  74,4,"Comci maa ɗin, laɓɓinaa"
  74,5,"Sanamuuji ɗin, woɗɗito-ɗaa"
  74,6,Wata a okkir fii heɓugol ko ɓuri ɗum
  74,7,"Ko fii Joomi maa, muññortaa"
  74,8,Si wuttaama ka allaandu
  74,9,"haray nden ñalnde woni, ñalaande sattunde"
  74,10,"e hoore heeferɓe ɓen, nde wanaa newiinde"
  74,11,Accidam e mo Mi tagi on kañun tun
  74,12,Mi waɗani mo jawdi ɗuuɗundi
  74,13,e ɓiɗɓe wonnduɓe e makko
  74,14,Mi yaññani mo yaññudee
  74,15,refti himo tamƴinoo nde mi ɓeydata
  74,16,Ɗum waɗataa ! Tawde o laatino sanndalɗiiɗo e Aayeeje Amen ɗen
  74,17,Aray Mi fawa mo lette sattuɗe
  74,18,"Kanko on, o miijiti o eɓɓindii"
  74,19,O huɗaama hono no o hoddiri
  74,20,Refti o huɗa hono o hoddiri
  74,21,Refti o ndaari
  74,22,Refti ñirɓanii o ɓeydi ñirɓinaade
  74,23,Refti o runtii hombo mawnikini
  74,24,"ɓe wi'a: \"Ɗum wonaali, si wanaa mbilewu ɓanngu ngu"
  74,25,Mbo wonah si wonah konngol aade
  74,26,Ma Mi naatnu mbo yiite saqara
  74,27,Hol ko anndin ma ko woni Saqara
  74,28,Nge heddatah nge accatah
  74,29,Sumoowe geece
  74,30,Ina e dow mannge sappa e jeenay
  74,31,"Men waɗaali aynooɓe yimɓe Yiite ngen, si wanaa Malaa'ika. Men waɗiraali limoore maɓɓe si wanaa jarraborgol yedduɓe ɓen, e fii yo henan okkaaɓe Defte ɓen, e fii no gomɗimɓe ɓen ɓeydora gomɗinal, e fii wata okkaaɓe Defte ɓen e gomɗimɓe ɓen sikkito; e fii yo ɓen ɓe ñawu woni e ɓerɗe mun e heeferɓe ɓen wi'u: \"Hara ko honɗum Allah faandorii e ngal misal?\" Ko wano non Allah majjinirta mo O muuyani, himo fewna kadi mo O muuyani. Hay gooto anndaa yeru koneeli Joomi maa ɗin, si wanaa Kanko. Ngen [Yiite] wonaali, si wanaa waaju wonannde neɗɗanke"
  74,32,Kono yo henane! Mi woondirii lewru ndun
  74,33,O woondiri jemma si mbo runtii ma
  74,34,E subaka si mbo fooyni
  74,35,Ko mbo gootel e mawɗi
  74,36,Ko nge jertinirde wonannde neɗɗanke
  74,37,"Wonannde on yiɗuɗo e mo'on, nde o yaccotoo maa nennoo"
  74,38,Wonkii kala ko faggii kon nanngirte
  74,39,Si wanaa yimɓe ñaamo ɓen
  74,40,"hiɓe e nder gese, hiɓe lamndondira"
  74,41,fii bomɓe ɓen
  74,42,ko hoɗum naadi on Saqara
  74,43,"Ɓen wi'a: \"Men jeyanooka e juulooɓe ɓen"
  74,44,men jeyanooka kadi e ñamminooɓe miskimɓe ɓen
  74,45,Hari men jumpidayno kadi e jumpooɓe ɓen
  74,46,Hari kadi men fennayno fii ñalaande njoɓdi nden
  74,47,"Haa [maayde] yananaande nden arani men"
  74,48,Nafataaɓe tefoore tefooɓe
  74,49,Hol ko waɗi ɓe sirkuɓe na ɗuurno Quraana
  74,50,Hoɓe mba*i e bamɗi laawatooɗi na ndoga
  74,51,Dokɗi mbaroodi
  74,52,Gooto e mum en fof na faaala totteede ɗeri caraaɗi
  74,53,Alah woni koɓe kulaani laakara
  74,54,Alah ɗuum ko ciftanirgol
  74,55,Ko kala faalaaɗo waactaroo mbo o waaccaroo mbo
  74,56,"ɓe mbaactaaka si wonah Alla na haaja, ko Kanko woni kaanduɗo e huleede ko Kanko woni kaanduɗo e yaafaade"
  75,1,Mbeɗa woondira ñande ndarnga
  75,2,Mbeɗa woondira fittaandu felooru
  75,3,Mbela aade sikkat Min ndenndintah ƴi*e makko
  75,4,Oho kay mbeɗa Min kattani fotndude gulle peɗeeli makko
  75,5,Kono aade yiɗi konde o wonata saay yeeso ka yeeso makko
  75,6,"Hiɓe lamndoo : \"Ko honnde woni Ñalaande njoɓdi kuuɗe"
  75,7,Si yitere majii
  75,8,Lewru nanngaa
  75,9,Naange e lewru ndenndina
  75,10,Ndeen aade wi*a hoɗo dogirde woni
  75,11,Alah dogdu alah e oon ñalngu
  75,12,Koto joom ma ñande heen nwoni ruttorde
  75,13,Aade na habre ñande heen ko ardini e golle e ko o leelni
  75,14,Ko woni ko aade na seedii e fittaandu makko
  75,15,Hay si o addii ngantuuji makko
  75,16,Woto dillin heen ɗemngal Ma haa njaawnaɗa e hembo
  75,17,Ko Minen woodani renndinde mbo e jannginde mbo Ma
  75,18,Si Min njanngii mbo rew e jande makko
  75,19,Refti ko e Amen fawi firde mbo
  75,20,Alah woni ko hoɗon ƴiɗi aduna jaawɗo ko gasata
  75,21,Accon laakara
  75,22,Geece malaaɓe ñande heen na fooyni
  75,23,Hoɗe ndaara faade e joom mum en
  75,24,E geece ñirɓaniiɗe ñande heen
  75,25,Hoɗe cikka ma telline e mum en musiiba mawɗo
  75,26,Alah sindu yottiima bororde
  75,27,Wi*e hombo moccata
  75,28,O yananee ko ɗuum woni ceergol e aduna
  75,29,Korlal fiilto e korlal
  75,30,Ka joom ma ñande heen nwoni ruttorde
  75,31,O goonɗinaani o juulaani
  75,32,Kono o fennu o ɗuurnii
  75,33,Refti o yahi ka koreeji makko hombo wasoo
  75,34,Halkaare woodaniima e halkaare
  75,35,Refti halkaare woodanii ma e halkaare
  75,36,Mbela aade sikku o accete hombo duda
  75,37,Mbela o wonaana toɓɓe maniyyu yuppateende e rannga
  75,38,Refti o wonti heɗɗere O tagi O fonndi
  75,39,O waɗI heen kuɓe dewel e gorel
  75,40,Mbela Oon hattanaani wuurtinde maayɓe
  76,1,Mbela arii e aade tumo e yonta nde o wonaana hay huunde jantateende
  76,2,Min tagii aade e toɓɓere jillunde ndiyam gorko e debbo Min kumpitoo mbo Min laatini mbo nanoowo ji*oowo
  76,3,Min peewnii mbo e laawol o yetta wollo o yedda
  76,4,Pellet Min keblinii heeferbe callalle e tonngi e yiite
  76,5,Pellet ɗigguɓe ɓe na yara e kaas jilluɗo kaafuur
  76,6,Seewnde nde jiyaaɓe Alla ɓallinaaɓe njarata hoɓe ilnande ilnugol
  76,7,Hoɓe kuuɓna takkere hoɓe kula ñalawma mbo bone mum na caroo
  76,8,Hoɓe ñammina ñamri wondude e yiɗde ndi miskiin e alyatiime e dahaaɗo
  76,9,Min ñamminirta mon ko sabi Alla Min faalaaka e mon njoɓdi wonah yetteede
  76,10,Pellet min kuli ummaade e joomi amen ko ñalawma nyirɓiniiɗo cattuɗo tumminaare
  76,11,Alla reeniɓe e bone oon ñalawma O okkiɓe pummam labaɗam e weltaare
  76,12,Alla yoɓiri ɓe koɓe muñi ko aljanna e hariir
  76,13,Hoɓe tuugnii e fotooyji ɓe yi*atah heen naange wonah jaangol cattungol
  76,14,Na ɓadi e dow mum en ɗowdi mammba ɓesnaaɗe mum na eeltanaaɓe eeltegol
  76,15,Ina taarneeɓe ngennduwon kaalis e kaasyon na feewnira weer
  76,16,Kaaseeje kaalis hoɗe potndira potndegol
  76,17,Hoɓe njarnee kaas njilludi mum ko janjabiil
  76,18,Seewnde na e hembo na inne Sal sabiil
  76,19,Sukaaɓe saasnaaɓe na mbanngo e mum en si a yi*iiɓe cikka ko ɓe lu*u lu*u caraaɗo
  76,20,Si a yi*i toon yi*a neema e laamu manngu
  76,21,Ina e dow mum en comci sundus ɗi mbaadi haaka hecco e istabraq ɓe ɓoorna jawe kaalis joom mum en yarnaɓe njaram laaɓɗam
  76,22,Pellet ɗum wonanii mon njoɓdi golle mon kadi golle mon ngoniina mantaaɗe
  76,23,Ko Minen tigi tellini Quraana e dow ma tellingol
  76,24,Muny e ñaawoore joom Ma woto ɗofto e mum en bakkadinɗo wolla keefeero
  76,25,janta inne joom ma subaka e kikiiɗa
  76,26,E jemma he sujjan Mbo cubahinanɗaa Mbo jemma juutɗo
  76,27,Pellet ɓe na njiɗi nguurndam aduna yaawɗam gasde ɓe acca caggal mum en ñalawma nisɗo
  76,28,Ko Minen tagi on Min cemmbini terɗo si Min haajaama Min gostoroo on nandadiiɓe mon gostogol
  76,29,Ko nde woni waaju goongo kala faalaaɗo daɗde nanngira faade e joomiiko ruttorde
  76,30,On paaletaake si wonah Alla haaje pellet Alla ko Ganndo ko ñeeño
  76,31,Hombo naatna mbo O welaa e yurmeene Makko O heblanii tooñɓe ɓe lepte muusɗe
  77,1,O woondirii keneeli dewandirɗi hono siiru puccu
  77,2,E bippooji bippugol
  77,3,E carooji cargolo
  77,4,E ceerndooji ceerndugol
  77,5,E tellinooji wahyu
  77,6,Gantingol wollo jeertingol
  77,7,"ko podante ɗon ko, ko goongo"
  77,8,Si koode ɗe momtaama
  77,9,Si kammu o huuftaama
  77,10,Si pelle ɗe nawaama
  77,11,Saanga Nelaaɓe kappana waktu
  77,12,E ñalawma dirtinaaɗo
  77,13,Wonande ñalngu ceerndugol
  77,14,Holko anndin ma ñalngu ceerndugol
  77,15,"haray nden ñalnde, bone woodanii fennuɓe ɓen"
  77,16,Mbela Min kalkaani adinooɓe ɓe
  77,17,Refti Min ndewni heen sakkatiiɓe ɓe
  77,18,Ko hono nih Min mbaɗata bonɓe ɓe
  77,19,"haray nden ñalnde, bone woodanii fennuɓe ɓen"
  77,20,Mbela Min tagaani mon e ndiyam koyɗam
  77,21,Min mbaɗi ɗam e rannga huɓandiinga
  77,22,Haa e happu ganndaaɗo
  77,23,Min koddiri mbo heskey ɓe Hoddirooɓe
  77,24,"haray nden ñalnde, bone woodanii fennuɓe ɓen"
  77,25,Mbela Min mbaɗaani leydi coomoori mon
  77,26,Wuurɓe e maayɓe
  77,27,Min mbaɗi e hendi penɗe toowɗe Min njarni mon ndiyam mbelɗam
  77,28,"haray nden ñalnde, bone woodanii fennuɓe ɓen"
  77,29,Pokkitane faade ko pennatnaɗon
  77,30,Pokkitane faade e ɗowdi ndi ɗemɗe tati
  77,31,Ndi ɗowdintah nafatah e lew lewndu
  77,32,Honge werlo peete mawe hono kuɓeeje
  77,33,Elle koɗe geloobi coooyi
  77,34,"haray nden ñalnde, bone woodanii fennuɓe ɓen"
  77,35,E o ñalngu ɓe kaalatah
  77,36,Ɓe cakkittaake saba ɓe ngantina
  77,37,"haray nden ñalnde, bone woodanii fennuɓe ɓen"
  77,38,O ko ñalngu ceerndugol Min ndenndinii on wondude e adiiɓe ɓe
  77,39,Si tawii hoɗon njogii feere pewjanee kam
  77,40,"haray nden ñalnde, bone woodanii fennuɓe ɓen"
  77,41,"Pellet, gomɗuɓe ɓen wonii e ɗowdiiji e ɓulli"
  77,42,E ɓesnaaɗe koɓe tuuyate
  77,43,"[Ɓe wi'anee] : \"Ñaamee yarone, ko newi moɗdu, sabu kon ko gollaynoɗon"
  77,44,Ko non woni ko Men warjorta moƴƴimɓe ɓen
  77,45,"haray nden ñalnde, bone woodanii fennuɓe ɓen"
  77,46,ñaame ndakmitaɗon setta ko on bannddiiji
  77,47,"haray nden ñalnde, bone woodanii fennuɓe ɓen"
  77,48,Siɓe wiyaama ndukƴe ɓe ndukƴatah
  77,49,"haray nden ñalnde, bone woodanii fennuɓe ɓen"
  77,50,Honde yeewtere caggal oon ɓe goonɗinta
  78,1,Kol ko ɓee naamnandirta
  78,2,Ko faati e kabaaru mawɗo
  78,3,Mboɓe luuri e mum
  78,4,"Alah wonah noon, maɓe nganndu"
  78,5,Refti yaama maɓe nganndu
  78,6,Mbela Min mbaɗaani leydi ndaɗɗudi keblaandi
  78,7,E pelleɗe ngona penɗe
  78,8,Min tagi on kuɓe
  78,9,Min mbaɗi ɗoyngol mon fooftere
  78,10,Min mbaɗi jemma o ko sutura
  78,11,Min mbaɗi ñalawma ko yiilaraade nguura
  78,12,Min mahi dow mon jeeɗiɗi cattuɗi
  78,13,Min mbaɗi lampu jalbuɗo kuɓɓam
  78,14,Min tellini ummaade e duule ndiyam njuppajam sanne
  78,15,Ngam Min njaltina heen gabbe e puɗi
  78,16,E gese piilandirɗe
  78,17,"Pellet, ko ñalaande Senndindiro ngon, laatinooma ko saatinaa"
  78,18,Ñande allaadu ndu wutta ma on ngardu pelle pelle
  78,19,Kammu on udditee mbo laato dame
  78,20,Pelle ɗe yahnaa ɗe ngonta merere
  78,21,Pellet Yiite jahannama wonti tommborde
  78,22,Nge wonanii bewɓe ɓe ruttorde
  78,23,Ma ɓe ñiiɓ toon dummunaaji
  78,24,ɓe meeɗatah toon ɓuuɓol wolla ndiyam ɓuuɓɗam
  78,25,Si wonah patɗam ƴiiƴiiri
  78,26,Njobdi kawrundi e koɓe ngonno ko
  78,27,Pellet ɓe ngoniina ɓe njoortaaki haasboore
  78,28,ɓe pennii aayeeje Amen pennugol
  78,29,Kala huunde min tonngirii nde binndol
  78,30,Meeɗe Min ɓeydantah on si wonah lepte
  78,31,Pellet na woodani hulɓe Alla ɓe foolirde
  78,32,Gese e inabeeje
  78,33,E ƴoolnuɓe giƴiraaɓe
  78,34,E kaas sanngara keewɗo
  78,35,"Ɓe nanataa nder toon haala meere, wanaa ko bakkondiŋta"
  78,36,Ko njoɓdi ummaade ka Alla e dokke keƴɗe
  78,37,jom kammu e leydi e ko woni hakkunde mum en jurmtooɗo Mbo ɓe ngalah e dow Mum haala
  78,38,Ñande jibriil ummii tawa malayka en na waɗi sappeeli ɓe haalatah si wonah mbo Alla sakkitani o haala ko feewi
  78,39,Ko oon woni ñalngu goongo kala faalaaɗo daɗde nanngira joomiiko ruttorde
  78,40,Min njeertinii on lepte ɓadiiɗe ñande aade ndaari ko juuɗe mum mbaɗno keefeero o wiya haaniina mi woniina leydi
  79,1,Alla woondirii malayka en pooɗooji pittaali pooɗgol cattungol
  79,2,Alla woondirii malayka en ittatɗi pittaali e newuya
  79,3,Alla woondirii lummbatooɗi lummbagol
  79,4,Alla woondarii daɗandirooji daɗndirgol
  79,5,E Alla woondirii yiilayɗi yamiroore
  79,6,ñande dimmbii dimmbatnde
